Dialogue: 4,0:00:53.76,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就回厨房了? 快把菜放下
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.76,0:00:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Straight back to the kitchen? Just leave the vegetables.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样不行，去休息吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This won't do. Go take some rest.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:59.96,0:01:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.96,0:01:00.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I do?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我不进厨房，这里就不像是家
Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Till I don't enter the kitchen, it doesn't feel like home.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过来炒菜，我马上回来
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Watch this, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1000卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's 1000 rupees.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德一定有计划，对吧? 很快就会解决的
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai is planning something, right? It will all work out soon.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:31.56,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要去斯里兰卡找份工作
Dialogue: 3,0:01:31.56,0:01:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm getting a job... in Sri Lanka.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直接去斯里兰卡？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the way to Sri Lanka?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我总不能在家里无所事事吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't keep sitting idle at home, can I?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:41.80,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在外面打工那么努力... 还要做所有的家务事..
Dialogue: 3,0:01:41.80,0:01:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You work so hard at the parlour... and then all the household chores...
Dialogue: 4,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说完了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.84,0:01:46.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you done?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}打工赚的钱足够经营这个家了，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The parlour is paying enough to run the house, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我喜欢在那里工作
Dialogue: 3,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I like working there.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们下个月要给我涨工资
Dialogue: 3,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They're increasing my salary next month.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听我说
Dialogue: 3,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是还跟哈尔沙德说
Dialogue: 3,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Weren't you the one telling Harshad Bhai...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时间能治愈一切？
Dialogue: 3,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that time is a great healer?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，给时间个机会
Dialogue: 3,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So then, time needs some time.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要两分钟，爸爸晚餐很快好了
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just two minutes, Pappa. Dinner is almost ready.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还欠苏雷什 · 巴海多少钱？
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much do we still owe Suresh Bhai?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}损失了一百万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a loss of 10 lakhs.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还了三千七百万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We've returned three, seven lakhs are pending.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当一个人在家里有了金子..
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When one has gold at home...
Dialogue: 4,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才能睡得安稳
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...one sleeps peacefully.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为我们的长辈为什么积累黄金？
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why do you think our elders collected gold?
Dialogue: 4,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是为了当艰难时刻来临时..
Dialogue: 3,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So when hard times come...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他们可以...-兄弟，别担心
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...they can... - Shanti Bhai, don't worry at all.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:14.72,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德和阿什温就像我的家人一样
Dialogue: 3,0:03:14.72,0:03:18.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad and Ashwin are like family to me.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，但我警告过哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. But I had warned Harshad...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要小心
Dialogue: 3,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to be careful.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道的... 在下雨的时候..
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know how it is... When it rains...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使你有伞
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...even if you have an umbrella...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你还是有可能在光滑的路上摔倒
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you can still fall on a slippery road.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是唯一一个亏钱的，整个市场都在下滑
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not the only one, the entire market has slipped.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当天上下着钱的时候，没有人会打开雨伞
Dialogue: 3,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And when it was raining money, no one bothered opening their umbrellas.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 每个人都忙着淋湿-但现在所有的东西都被冲走了！
Dialogue: 3,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Everyone was busy getting drenched. - But everything has washed away now!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么都没有了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- There's nothing left.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们现在和我们家的金子坐在这里！
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are sitting here with our family gold!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请冷静..
Dialogue: 3,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please calm down...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(苏雷什)“这是常有的事”
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Suresh] 'It happens.'
Dialogue: 4,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，苏雷什兄弟
Dialogue: 3,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm sorry, Suresh Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏雷什兄弟，这些是我的财产证明
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Suresh Bhai, these are my property papers.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这套公寓和这块金子..
Dialogue: 3,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The flat and this gold...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}应该能抵七十万的债务
Dialogue: 3,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...should cover your seven lakhs.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在说什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you saying, Shanti Bhai?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不需要这些财产证明
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no need for these property papers.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}钱又不会跑？
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The money isn't running away, is it?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那样的话，你为什么不重新启动我们的交易帐户呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, in that case, why don't you restart our trading account?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也许可以早点还给你
Dialogue: 3,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I might be able to pay you back sooner.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 3,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look Harshad...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在三年内赚了三十万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you earned three lakhs in three years.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}却在10分钟内损失了100万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you lost 10 lakhs in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，很明显，股票市场不是那么容易..
Dialogue: 3,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, obviously the stock market is not that easy...
Dialogue: 4,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能让你马上就能进去开始印钱
Dialogue: 3,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you will get in and start minting right away.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:46.00,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，除非你还完这一百万，否则你的交易帐户就一直暂停
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.00,0:04:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, until you return the full amount, your trading account will remain suspended.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:52.28,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏雷什]“这个孩子很聪明，但他在跑起来之前”
Dialogue: 3,0:04:52.28,0:04:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Suresh] 'The boy is smart but he wants to charge ahead.'
Dialogue: 4,0:04:58.32,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要先学会走路..
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.32,0:05:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He needs to learn how to walk first...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么还没睡？
Dialogue: 3,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How come you're still up?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}睡不着
Dialogue: 3,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, well...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想我吃得太多了
Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I think I ate too much.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经吃了些消化药
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I did take some digestive.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你呢
Dialogue: 3,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You tell me.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么醒了？
Dialogue: 3,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you awake?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明天有个会议
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's a meeting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦我们的交易帐户重新开启
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once our trading account is up and running...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ... 然后看...-哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...then see... - Harshad.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你总是在逆潮游泳
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You always swim against the tide.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}白天做梦，晚上熬夜
Dialogue: 3,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You dream during the day and stay up at night.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:56.72,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}除非你保持清醒，你的交易账户就不会重启
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.72,0:06:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not like your trading account will restart if you stay awake.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去睡觉，好吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go to sleep. Okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你害怕了，是不是？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}害怕我们可能又要离开孟买了？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that we might have to leave Bombay again?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:19.72,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 不是那样的
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.72,0:06:23.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}爸爸
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pappa.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}永远不要对黑夜撒谎
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Never lie to the night.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}黑夜掌握着我们所有的秘密
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The night holds all our secrets.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的股票经纪人儿子..
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My stock-broker son...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么时候变成诗人了？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...when did you turn into a poet?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要我还活着..
Dialogue: 3,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会让孟买证券交易所离开我的视线
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I won't let Bombay Stock Exchange out of my sight.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交易所就在这里，在孟买
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And BSE is right here, in Bombay.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，爸爸，快去睡吧
Dialogue: 3,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So Mr. Shantilal, go sleep in peace.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，尚蒂拉尔先生... ..
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'So Mr. Shantilal...'
Dialogue: 4,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们早点知道的话，还可以把他送到医院去
Dialogue: 3,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Had we known earlier, we could've taken him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们怎么付得起医院的账单？
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And how would we afford the hospital bills?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许这样更好
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's for the better.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在睡梦中安详地去世
Dialogue: 3,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He passed away in his sleep peacefully.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他最放不下的是你
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He was most worried about you.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}担忧是通往火葬场的必经之路
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Worrying is a sure path to your pyre'.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是山特拉尔先生常说的话
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's what Mr. Shantilal used to say.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道电信公司和 Zenith 公司会迅速崛起
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I knew that Telco and Zenith would surge.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我本来可以赚一大笔钱的
Dialogue: 3,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I could have made a solid profit.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要去斯里兰卡找份工作
Dialogue: 3,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm getting a job in Sri Lanka.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在认真考虑
Dialogue: 3,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm seriously considering it.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在正是我需要你的时候，你却打算离开我？
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the time to stay together and you are also planning to leave me?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Also'?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}爸爸已经..
Dialogue: 3,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pappa has already...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有头脑，你知道我们可以做到的
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.48,0:10:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, we have the brains. You know we can do this.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经预测到了这些股票的涨跌
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I had predicted the rise and fall of all these shares.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个纸上交易..
Dialogue: 3,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This paper-trading...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像在街角的小店里看板球比赛
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is like watching cricket at a corner store...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后给加瓦斯卡指示
Dialogue: 3,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.61,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and giving instructions to Gavaskar.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你自己走上三柱门，就被保龄球打中了
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Step onto the wicket yourself, and you're bowled.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我有钱，我就不会比加瓦斯卡少了
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I had the money, I'd be no less than Gavaskar here.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我们没有钱！
Dialogue: 3,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we don't have the money!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德兄弟，好久不见
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Bhai, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来三杯好茶
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Three specials.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天我请客喝茶
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tea is on me today.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你上次给我的情报，效果很好
Dialogue: 3,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The tip you gave me last time, it worked wonders.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感谢上帝，我赚了很多钱
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By God's grace, I earned a lot.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许你已经厌倦了市场，但是请继续给我们提供情报
Dialogue: 3,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe you are fed up with the market... ...but don't stop giving us tips.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少我们的口袋会满满的！
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At least our pockets will be full!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你说什么?-嘿，维卡斯！
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Vikas] 'What say?' - Hey, Vikas!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来了! 把茶给他们，记在我的账上
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Coming! Give them the tea and put it on my tab.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们提供咨询服务吧
Dialogue: 3,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's start consulting.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么?-一家咨询公司
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What? - A consultancy firm.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说真的吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我们没钱..
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, we don't have money...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的脸也不会吸引任何人
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and our faces aren't going to attract any.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，让我们的大脑开始工作吧
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, let's put our brains to work.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们能把5卢比变成10卢比，我们至少能赚50派沙的佣金
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we can turn five rupees into ten for anybody we'll make at least 50 paise in commission.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股市崩盘之后，是一个非常危险的地方
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After the crash, the stock market is a very risky place.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我觉得这不是个好提议-不..
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I don't think it's a good proposal. - No...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是股市的错..
Dialogue: 3,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's not the stock market's fault...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就像一场蛇梯棋游戏
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that it is like a game of snakes and ladders.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:06.76,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听我说完，就这一次，掷骰子..
Dialogue: 3,0:12:06.76,0:12:10.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hear me out Dhruv Bhai, just this once, roll the dice...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁知道呢，说不定你正好落在通往顶端的梯子上呢！
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who knows, you might just land on the ladder to the top!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果再次下跌怎么办？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what if it slips again?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能再跌多少？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How much lower can it slip, Dhruv Bhai?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场已经跌到谷底，唯一的出路就是上涨
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market is at its rock-bottom. The only way now, is up.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的公司是一家新公司
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And look, ours is a new company.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不会因为一分钱就毁了我们的名声，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We won't ruin our reputation for the sake of pennies, will we?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这比市场崩溃的风险更大
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's riskier than the market crashing.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 阿什温，告诉我真相-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Ashwin, tell me the truth. - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是你牺牲的第一只羔羊吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Am I the first lamb you're sacrificing?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 水牛-什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Buffalo. - What?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 对牛弹琴-什么意思？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Singing to a buffalo. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“真的，阿什温! ”
Dialogue: 3,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Really, Ashwin!'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和一个对市场不感兴趣的人谈话有什么意义呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's the point of talking to someone who is not interested in the markets?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这难道不像对牛弹琴吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't it like singing to a buffalo?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没告诉过你吗? 这些特许会计师生活在对红线的恐惧中
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didn't I tell you? These Chartered Accountants live in fear of the red line.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是未来的客户，哈尔沙德
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's a future client, Harshad.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你怎么能这么说我们的客户?-什么客户？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- How can you say such things about a client? - What client?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:53.48,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}牛还没出生，你就开始用牛奶庆祝？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.48,0:12:58.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The buffalo isn't born yet, and you're celebrating with buttermilk?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}客户是投资人
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A client is one who invests money.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他对任何投资都不感兴趣
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he is not interested in making any investment.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你找到一个客户了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you managed to find even a single client?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我找到一个客户，他投资了45万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've found a client who's investing 4.5 lakhs.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你就保持安静
Dialogue: 3,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'So, you just stay quiet.'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:07.88,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，别理他，他是个急性子
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.88,0:13:11.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Dhruv Bhai, ignore him, he's hot-headed.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请不要让这件事影响我们的友谊
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please don't let this come in the way of our friendship.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，这是你的钱，你的愿望
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look. It's your money, your wish.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 毕竟，谁挥动棍子，谁就能得到水牛-嘿！
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- After all, he who wields the stick, gets the buffalo. - Hey!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请不要再说那些关于“水牛”的格言了
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.68,0:13:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stop with the 'buffalo' sayings. Please.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我还没有拒绝
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I haven't refused yet.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}10万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One lakh.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以投资10万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can invest up to one lakh.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“如果你把我带到梯子那儿，我们就再滚一次”
Dialogue: 3,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dhruv] 'If you get me to the ladder, we'll roll again.'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你那些水牛说的话可能会让我们损失惨重! ”
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ashwin] 'Your buffalo sayings could have cost us heavily!'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:46.88,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是也一样! 你设下了一个45万卢比的陷阱
Dialogue: 3,0:13:46.88,0:13:51.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are no less! You laid a good '4.5 lakh' trap.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那不是陷阱，我们真的有四十五万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That wasn't a trap, we do have 4.5 lakhs.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿! 过来
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey! Come here.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从哪来的钱？
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}From where?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我岳父岳母给的-什么意思？
Dialogue: 3,0:13:58.24,0:14:00.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- From my in-laws. - Meaning?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和迪皮卡的父亲谈过了
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning, I have spoken to Deepika's father.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你岳父?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Your father-in-law? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但是...-是从他的退休基金里拿的
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But... - It was from his retirement fund.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果财富女神敲我的门，我怎么会不开门呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If the Goddess of wealth knocks at my door, won't I open it?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他主动提出，我接受了
Dialogue: 3,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He offered, I accepted.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁知道呢，我岳父的钱可能会给我们带来成功
Dialogue: 3,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And who knows, my father-in-law's money might bring us success.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}到底什么是成功? 失败后的下一个篇章
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is success, after all? The next chapter after failure.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说得好，我的塔拉克 · 梅塔！
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well said, my Taarak Mehta!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 3,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin Mehta.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“高摩，这是什么意思? ”
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Suresh] 'Growmore. What does it mean?'
Dialogue: 4,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“高”意味着“进步” ，“摩”意味着“很多”
Dialogue: 3,0:14:32.28,0:14:35.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Grow' means 'to progress'. 'More' means 'a lot'.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进步很多，繁荣很多
Dialogue: 3,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Progress a lot. Prosper a lot.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在英文名字很流行，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}English names are all the rage these days, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看苏雅塔钢铁公司他们改名为种马钢铁..
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at Sujata Steels. They changed their name to Stallion Steels...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两个月后，它们的股价从7卢比涨到了12卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and in 2 months, their price rose from seven to twelve rupees.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:51.56,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们更倾向于相信英文名字，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:51.56,0:14:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People tend to trust English names more, isn't it?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经把帐算清了
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, I've settled the accounts.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们还欠你一点... 很快会还给你的
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We owe you a little more... We'll return it soon.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没必要担心
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么告诉我，你未来的计划是什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So tell me, what are your future plans?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有一些投资人，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have some investors, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是..
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What I mean is...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}投资需要经纪人对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to invest, you'd need a broker, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，我们会在某个地方成为次级经纪人
Dialogue: 3,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's right. We'll become sub-brokers somewhere.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在别的地方? 为什么不在这里？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Somewhere? Why not here?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你已经暂停了我们的交易账户，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you've suspended our trading account, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以很明显我们不能在这里做次级经纪人
Dialogue: 3,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So obviously we can't be sub-brokers here.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的交易帐户今天恢复
Dialogue: 3,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your trading account resumes today.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要想太多，今天是吉祥的日子
Dialogue: 3,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't think too much. Today is an auspicious day.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧从今天开始你就是我的代理人
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.44,0:15:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. From today, I make you my sub-broker.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有别的事吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anything else?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么…
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的地址在哪里？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's your address?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我到哪里去找你喝杯茶？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where do I visit you for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在这栋楼里有八个办公室..
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have eight offices in this building...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你很幸运..
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you are very lucky...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你父亲的旧办公室还可以使用
Dialogue: 3,0:16:08.76,0:16:12.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that your father's old office is available.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道这看起来有点乱
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know it looks a bit messy.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，我会打扫干净，焕然一新
Dialogue: 3,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But, I'll get it cleaned and it'll be spanking new.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}租金是多少？
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's the rent?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}以前的房客付250卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Landlord] 'The previous tenant used to pay 250 rupees.'
Dialogue: 4,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们就像一家人，租金是可以商量的
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'You're like family. It's negotiable.'
Dialogue: 4,0:16:25.52,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}重要的是所有的纺织品贸易商在这里都有办公室..
Dialogue: 3,0:16:25.52,0:16:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's important is that all textile traders have offices here...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你可以得到你需要的一切，比如纽扣，线，针..
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can get everything you need. Buttons, thread, needles...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们经营的不是纺织品
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our business is not textiles.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你父亲..
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But your father...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他当时是做纺织生意的
Dialogue: 3,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he did run a textile business then...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们是在股票市场
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but we are in the share market.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.36,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德，他开价500卢比租金和5000押金
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.36,0:17:10.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, he is quoting 500 rupees rent and a deposit of 5000.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管多少钱，我们就租这里
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whatever it is, let's take it.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么要搬进你爸爸的办公室？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why did you have to move into that same office?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个办公室什么也没给我们
Dialogue: 3,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That office has given us nothing.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，它夺走了我们拥有的一切
Dialogue: 3,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, it took away everything we had.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 请不要担心...-我为什么不应该担心？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Please don't worry... - Why shouldn't I worry?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 叫什么来着? 坏...-坏运气
Dialogue: 3,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What is it called? Bad... - Bad luck.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 对吧?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不会出任何差错
Dialogue: 3,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nothing will go wrong.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那里所有的商人都在赚钱
Dialogue: 3,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All traders there are minting money.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来，读读这篇文章
Dialogue: 3,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here, read this paper.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我不看-你的星座是什么? 你不是白羊座的吗
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I don't want to. - What's your zodiac? Aren't you an Aries...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿! 你一大早去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey! Where did you go early in the morning?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:50.04,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}调查市场
Dialogue: 3,0:17:50.04,0:17:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fact-finding.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 调查 -调查? 调查茶叶？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Research. - Research? Researching tea?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们现在要开茶摊了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are we starting a tea stall now?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 妈妈，给我倒杯茶-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Mummy, get me a cup of tea please? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们应该投资茶叶
Dialogue: 3,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We should invest in tea.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:05.88,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿! 就因为一个卖茶的把价格提高了50派沙..
Dialogue: 3,0:18:05.88,0:18:09.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey! Just because a tea seller increased the price by 50 paise...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在你认为股票市场会因此而繁荣吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...now you think the stock market will boom because of this?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:11.96,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是在说零钱，我刚刚和来自肯尼亚的哈里什谈过
Dialogue: 3,0:18:11.96,0:18:16.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not talking about loose change. I've just spoken to Harish, the one from Kenya.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道世界上哪个国家生产的茶叶最多吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know which country produces the most tea in the world?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 中国-不是！
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- China. - Rubbish!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 为什么?-是非洲
Dialogue: 3,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Why? - It's Africa.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界上百分之三十以上的茶叶产自非洲
Dialogue: 3,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}More than thirty percent of the world's tea is produced in Africa.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}斯里兰卡排名第二，印度排名第四
Dialogue: 3,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sri Lanka is in second position and India comes fourth.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很高兴知道这一点，但这跟我们有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's good to know but how does it matter to us?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这很重要，兄弟
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It matters a lot, brother.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Mavtho"改变了整个游戏规则
Dialogue: 3,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mavtho has changed the whole game this year.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么是 Mavtho？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's Mavtho?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}非季节性降雨
Dialogue: 3,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Unseasonal rainfall.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这使得非洲的茶叶产量大幅下降
Dialogue: 3,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This has dropped tea production in Africa considerably.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:44.36,0:18:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is it?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 现在他们不能满足需求了-没错
Dialogue: 3,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Now they won't be able to meet the demand. - Correct.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，谁会从中受益呢
Dialogue: 3,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, who is going to benefit from it? Uhh...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 印度-没错
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- India. - Yes, right.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这个，印度今年的茶叶出口量将翻一番
Dialogue: 3,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this, Indian tea exports are about to double this year.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 所以利润也会翻倍-翻倍
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So, the profits too will double. - Double.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 所以，我们应该大量投资塔塔茶叶公司-还有其他公司
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So, let's invest big in Tata Tea. - There are other companies too.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有哈里森、马拉雅拉姆、麦克劳德、拉塞尔
Dialogue: 3,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's Harrisons Malayalam... McLeod Russell.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}麦克劳德每年支付20% 的股息
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}McLeod pays a 20 percent dividend every year.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但它的股价只有14卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But its share price is only 14 rupees.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们投资它，一定会获利
Dialogue: 3,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we invest in it, we're sure to make a profit.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你的速度怎么样？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what's your speed?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我每分钟能打80个字
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I can type 80 words per minute.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，你有打字机吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. Do you own a typewriter?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有，先生，你得提供一台打字机
Dialogue: 3,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, sir. You will have to give me a typewriter.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.84,0:19:33.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, no...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你想在这里工作，你就得有自己的打字机
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you want to work here, you'll have to get your own typewriter.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以输入印地语，英语，Gujarati 和马拉地语
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can type in Hindi, English, Gujarati and Marathi.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，雷贝罗，坐下
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Rebello, sit down.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}雷贝罗，你的打字速度怎么样？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rebello, what's your typing speed?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 每分钟四十个 -才四十个？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Forty. - Just forty?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是的，先生 -我手写都比你快
Dialogue: 3,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes, sir. - I write faster than that by hand.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我会进步的，先生，我每天都在练习
Dialogue: 3,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I will improve, sir. I practice every day.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 在哪里练习?-在家里
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.24,0:19:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Where? - At home.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你有打字机吗? -有
Dialogue: 3,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Do you own a typewriter? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的拉瓦尔先生...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Dear Mr. Rawal...'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们高摩咨询公司想邀请您...”
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...we at Growmore Consultants would like to invite you...'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我们这里开一个交易账户
Dialogue: 3,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to open a trading account with us.'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“在这里，我们可以把你多余的钱…”
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.92,0:20:14.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Here we can park your surplus money into the stock markets...'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}放在我们的投资组合管理计划下投入股市
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...under our portfolio management scheme.'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的商业战略建立在这样一个信念之上:
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Our business strategy rests on the belief...'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可以为您提供优质服务和更高的回报
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that we can provide you with good service and higher returns.'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:27.68,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“哈尔沙德 · 梅塔敬上，来自高摩咨询”
Dialogue: 3,0:20:27.68,0:20:32.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Yours truly, Harshad Mehta for Growmore.'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil] 'What're you even saying?'
Dialogue: 4,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我告诉过你，我听不懂
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I told you, this would go past my head.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看到没? 我是对的
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See? I was right.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不明白
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎么能卖掉我没有的股份呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can I sell shares that I don't have?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这叫做空？ -也许吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- It's called selling short. - That may be so.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 怎么做到的?-你没有股份..
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But how is it done? - Look, you don't have the shares...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是管理你交易账户的经纪人有很多股
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but the broker who handles your trading account has plenty shares.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们假设... 信实公司今天股价是100卢比..
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's assume... Reliance is 100 rupees today...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得它可能会跌下来
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and you think it might drop.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以你让你的经纪人以你的名义卖出10股，每股100卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So you ask your broker to sell 10 shares on your behalf, for 100 rupees each.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以他卖10股，每股100卢比他赚多少钱？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So he sells 10 shares for 100 rupees each. How much does he make?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一千卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A thousand rupees.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那1000块是我的吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Will that 1000 be mine?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还不是，没那么简单
Dialogue: 3,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not yet. It's not so easy.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 首先你得换掉他卖给你的股票对吧?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:21:09.56,0:21:12.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- First, you have to replace the shares that he sold for you, correct? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种结算周期在股票市场持续14天
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this settlement cycle lasts 14 days in the share market.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:16.36,0:21:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，在这14天里，股价可能会波动
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.36,0:21:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now in these 14 days, the share price can fluctuate.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可能会达到110,120,80,90等等
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It could go to 110, 120, 80, 90, etcetera.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在假设股票价值达到80..
Dialogue: 3,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now say, the day the share value is at 80...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你让你的经纪人帮你买十股
Dialogue: 3,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...you ask your broker to buy ten shares for you...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他花了多少钱买的？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how much does he pay for them?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 800?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 800? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是所谓的“简化交易”
Dialogue: 3,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is called 'squaring off a transaction'.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:34.28,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}1000美元卖出，800美元买回，利润是多少？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:34.28,0:21:37.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sold for 1000, bought back at 800, what's the profit?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}200? 200的利润？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}200? A profit of 200?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不完全是，还要扣除一些佣金
Dialogue: 3,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not entirely, some is deducted as commission.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}剩下的就是你的了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The rest is yours.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就像打板球一样，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is like betting in cricket, isn't it?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你把赌注押在可能会输的那一方，输了你就赢了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:47.52,0:21:50.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You bet on the losing team, the team loses and you make a profit.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果球队赢了呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But what if the team wins?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果股价上涨怎么办？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if the share price goes up?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果你知道球队的历史..
Dialogue: 3,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if you know the team's history...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}球员的记录，以及球场的状况等等
Dialogue: 3,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the player's record, the condition of the pitch...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就不是赌博，而是经过深思熟虑的预测
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then it's not betting. It's a calculated prediction.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:04.32,0:22:06.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:09.40,0:22:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要相信哈尔沙德敏锐的商业头脑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.40,0:22:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Trust Harshad's sharp business sense.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:12.12,0:22:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它是超越所有人的最佳头脑
Dialogue: 3,0:22:12.12,0:22:13.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It slices past the best of them.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:14.24,0:22:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[普拉那夫]‘普通客户，重点客户……’
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.24,0:22:18.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pranav] 'Plain papadum, pickled papadum.'
Dialogue: 4,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘朴实的客户，街上的客户... ’朴实的意思是... 家人和朋友..
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Plain papadum, pickled papad...' Plain meaning... family and friends..
Dialogue: 4,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有街上的客户? 你在外面加的联系人
Dialogue: 3,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And pickled? The contacts you add outside.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}半年过去了，你却只有几个本土客户
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In six months, all you have are a few home-grown clients...
Dialogue: 4,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有一个是从别的地方来的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and not a single pickled one from elsewhere.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你这样还能走多远？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How far will you go like this?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉那夫兄弟，我对流动的客户没兴趣
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav Bhai, I am not interested in rolling papadums.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想直接煎一下，配上番茄洋葱一起吃
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to directly fry and eat them with a tomato-onion garnish.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:42.44,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你现在是在找公司客户吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.44,0:22:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you asking for corporate clients now?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:44.48,0:22:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你肯定能给我弄到一些，你现在对企业界很熟悉了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:44.48,0:22:47.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can surely get me a few. You're well-versed with the corporate world now.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:49.20,0:22:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想都别想，公司客户不会来这里的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.20,0:22:51.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't even think about it, Corporate clients won't come here.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:52.16,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是也有几只有钱的鸟，我们可以为他们撒一些种子
Dialogue: 3,0:22:52.16,0:22:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But there are a few wealthy birds. We can spread some Seed for them.
Dialogue: 4,0:22:55.48,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，他们不会给你的鸽子笼增光添彩
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.48,0:22:59.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But hey! They won't grace this pigeonhole of yours.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:01.60,0:23:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的贫穷将困扰他们富有的灵魂
Dialogue: 3,0:23:01.60,0:23:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your poverty will trouble their rich souls.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:08.56,0:23:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，你说怎样就怎样
Dialogue: 3,0:23:08.56,0:23:10.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. I'll do whatever you say.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的英语说得怎么样？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How well does English roll off your tongue?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:18.68,0:23:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的公司是刚成立不久的
Dialogue: 3,0:23:18.68,0:23:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My company is relatively new.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我对市场有新的看法
Dialogue: 3,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I have a fresh approach towards the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我一直为我所有的客户
Dialogue: 3,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've been consistently delivering 37 percent profit...
Dialogue: 4,0:23:25.64,0:23:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}保持着37% 的利润
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.64,0:23:27.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to all my clients for the last 10 months.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请看
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a look.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是才这么点钱，利润高又能怎样呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But the base capital is quite low. How does the profit matter?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这么说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, look at it this way. The glass is half full.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有没有见过一个10卢比的投资回报14卢比？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you ever seen a return of 14 rupees on an investment of 10?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不知不觉，一百万卢比就会变成一百四十万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:23:48.04,0:23:50.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before you know it, ten lakhs will turn into 14.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:51.40,0:23:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以轻而易举地为你提供纯粹的利润
Dialogue: 3,0:23:51.40,0:23:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can serve you pure profit on a platter.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:55.48,0:23:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场不是阿里巴巴的洞穴，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.48,0:23:57.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Share market isn't Ali Baba's cave, is it?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:58.48,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说“芝麻开门” ，宝藏的大门就会打开？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.48,0:24:01.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You'll say 'Open Sesame' and the door to the treasure will open?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:03.68,0:24:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}完全正确，这既不是洞穴，也不是魔法
Dialogue: 3,0:24:03.68,0:24:06.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're absolutely right. This is neither a cave nor is it magic.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是我们必须改变的观念
Dialogue: 3,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that's the very perception we have to change.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:09.24,0:24:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一切都是需要研究和分析的
Dialogue: 3,0:24:09.24,0:24:11.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, it's all about research and analysis.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:11.36,0:24:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只有进行适当的研究和分析，才能在市场上投资你的钱
Dialogue: 3,0:24:11.36,0:24:15.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We conduct proper research and analysis, and only then we invest your money in the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:15.96,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么样的研究？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:15.96,0:24:17.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What kind of research?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:17.40,0:24:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的研究是指公司的资产负债表，未来的计划..
Dialogue: 3,0:24:17.40,0:24:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By research I mean, the company's balance sheet, its future plans...
Dialogue: 4,0:24:20.96,0:24:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有一些只有少数人知道的重要机密信息
Dialogue: 3,0:24:20.96,0:24:24.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and some crucial confidential information that only a few know about.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}长话短说..
Dialogue: 3,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To cut a long story short...
Dialogue: 4,0:24:28.40,0:24:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上个月... 放松，小心点
Dialogue: 3,0:24:28.40,0:24:32.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Last month... Easy, be careful.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:32.96,0:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我一个月前告诉你..
Dialogue: 3,0:24:32.96,0:24:35.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if I had told you a month back...
Dialogue: 4,0:24:35.84,0:24:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度国家板球队将会赢得世界杯
Dialogue: 3,0:24:35.84,0:24:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to bet on the Indian cricket team because it's going to win the World Cup.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:38.80,0:24:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会这么做吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:38.80,0:24:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Would you have done it?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:40.08,0:24:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是现在看看，印度已经赢得了世界杯
Dialogue: 3,0:24:40.08,0:24:42.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But now look, India has won the World Cup.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:42.80,0:24:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在想想，那些在印度上下注的人..
Dialogue: 3,0:24:42.80,0:24:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now think about this. The ones who did bet on India...
Dialogue: 4,0:24:44.96,0:24:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们一定发了大财！
Dialogue: 3,0:24:44.96,0:24:46.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What a fortune they must have made!
Dialogue: 4,0:24:46.56,0:24:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}记住一件事，哈尔沙德..
Dialogue: 3,0:24:46.56,0:24:48.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Remember one thing. Harshad...
Dialogue: 4,0:24:49.08,0:24:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是交易所里的的卡皮尔・德夫（板球运动员？）
Dialogue: 3,0:24:49.08,0:24:51.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is the Kapil Dev of BSE.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:51.96,0:24:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别想太多了，让我们为此干杯
Dialogue: 3,0:24:51.96,0:24:54.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't think too much. Let's drink to this.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:55.28,0:24:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 干杯-干杯
Dialogue: 3,0:24:55.28,0:24:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 4,0:24:59.96,0:25:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过来，我有话跟你说
Dialogue: 3,0:24:59.96,0:25:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come here. I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:02.28,0:25:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}失陪，先生们
Dialogue: 3,0:25:02.28,0:25:03.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Carry on gentlemen.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:05.40,0:25:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我再也忍受不了了，所以就跳了进去，对不起
Dialogue: 3,0:25:05.40,0:25:08.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I couldn't bear it any longer, so I jumped in. Sorry.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:09.84,0:25:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在我的阿里巴巴，去让你的40个盗贼和钱打交道吧..
Dialogue: 3,0:25:09.84,0:25:13.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now my Ali Baba, go keep your 40 thieves engaged with money...
Dialogue: 4,0:25:13.92,0:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去找我的宝贝们
Dialogue: 3,0:25:13.92,0:25:18.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll go get my honey...
Dialogue: 4,0:25:19.12,0:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}亲爱的，我讨厌眼泪但我喜欢欢呼声！
Dialogue: 3,0:25:19.12,0:25:24.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Darling, I hate tears But I love cheers!
Dialogue: 4,0:25:25.28,0:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}耶！
Dialogue: 3,0:25:25.28,0:25:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 4,0:25:28.32,0:25:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来，来..
Dialogue: 3,0:25:28.32,0:25:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come, come...
Dialogue: 4,0:25:30.60,0:25:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生们，来见见我的小蝴蝶
Dialogue: 3,0:25:30.60,0:25:33.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Gentlemen, meet my butterflies.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:33.52,0:25:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}蝴蝶们，去见见你们的大黄蜂
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.52,0:25:36.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Butterflies, meet your bumblebees.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:41.08,0:25:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么把腰带系这么紧? 现在是时候松开了
Dialogue: 3,0:25:41.08,0:25:43.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you tightening your trousers? It's time to loosen them now.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:44.68,0:25:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿！
Dialogue: 3,0:25:44.68,0:25:45.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey!
Dialogue: 4,0:25:51.44,0:25:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}废物
Dialogue: 3,0:25:51.44,0:25:52.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's completely useless.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你这个傻瓜！
Dialogue: 3,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're a fool!
Dialogue: 4,0:25:55.16,0:25:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你已经变成了一匹驮马
Dialogue: 3,0:25:55.16,0:25:57.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've become a workhorse.
Dialogue: 4,0:25:57.76,0:25:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}聪明一点！
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.76,0:25:59.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Be smarter!
Dialogue: 4,0:26:00.92,0:26:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么时候离开聚会的？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:00.92,0:26:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When did you leave the party?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:02.56,0:26:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我走之前没告诉你吗?-那么早？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:02.56,0:26:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Didn't I tell you before leaving? - That early?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:06.72,0:26:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我是个有家室的男人，我不能这么做-啊？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:06.72,0:26:09.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I'm a family man, I can't do this. - Huh?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:10.44,0:26:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我们有家庭，我们不能这么做
Dialogue: 3,0:26:10.44,0:26:13.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, we have families. We can't do this.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:13.36,0:26:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，家庭主妇们! 他们都是有家室的男人
Dialogue: 3,0:26:13.36,0:26:16.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey, family wallahs! All those were also family men.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:16.56,0:26:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温，这就是现在经营生意的方式，只有混在一起才能赚钱
Dialogue: 3,0:26:16.56,0:26:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ashwin, this is how you run a business. You will earn money only if you mingle.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:22.00,0:26:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其中四个人准备投资一百万卢比但是他..
Dialogue: 3,0:26:22.00,0:26:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Four of them were ready to invest ten lakhs, but him...
Dialogue: 4,0:26:26.64,0:26:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 顾家男人-就四个？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:26.64,0:26:28.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Family man. - Just four?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:28.84,0:26:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不是说有40个人吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:28.84,0:26:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Didn't you say there were 40 people?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这是重点吗?-看看这个
Dialogue: 3,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Pranav] 'How does it matter?' - Look at this.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:33.24,0:26:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}芝麻开门
Dialogue: 3,0:26:33.24,0:26:34.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Open Sesame.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:34.96,0:26:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:34.96,0:26:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is it?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:42.76,0:26:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“戈瓦尔丹”
Dialogue: 3,0:26:42.76,0:26:43.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Govardhan."
Dialogue: 4,0:26:45.20,0:26:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“戈尔丹达斯”
Dialogue: 3,0:26:45.20,0:26:46.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Gordhandas."
Dialogue: 4,0:26:47.60,0:26:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“马尼拉”
Dialogue: 3,0:26:47.60,0:26:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Manilal."
Dialogue: 4,0:26:48.96,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}”瓦桑特”
Dialogue: 3,0:26:48.96,0:26:49.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Vasant."
Dialogue: 4,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}瓦桑特给你钱了? ！
Dialogue: 3,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Vasant gave you money?!
Dialogue: 4,0:26:53.56,0:26:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿里巴巴和大盗，哈尔沙德和高摩投资
Dialogue: 3,0:26:53.56,0:26:57.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ali Baba and thieves galore, Harshad and Growmore.
Dialogue: 4,0:26:59.96,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟我击个掌
Dialogue: 3,0:26:59.96,0:27:01.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give me a high five.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:06.44,0:27:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}达拉尔女士你知道..
Dialogue: 3,0:27:06.44,0:27:08.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ms. Dalal, do you know...
Dialogue: 4,0:27:08.72,0:27:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}孟买证券交易所有多少层吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:08.72,0:27:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...how many floors there are in the Bombay Stock Exchange?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:14.00,0:27:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}28层
Dialogue: 3,0:27:14.00,0:27:15.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Twenty-eight.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:16.24,0:27:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这28层楼之间跑来跑去
Dialogue: 3,0:27:16.24,0:27:18.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Running between these 28 floors and gathering...
Dialogue: 4,0:27:18.80,0:27:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每天的每一点信息都可能是你的工作
Dialogue: 3,0:27:18.80,0:27:21.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...every bit of information every day could be your job.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:21.68,0:27:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在听起来还令人兴奋吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:21.68,0:27:23.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Does it still sound exciting?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:24.12,0:27:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 3,0:27:24.12,0:27:25.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:26.00,0:27:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且，我现在的工作也要经常到处跑，所以这根本不是问题
Dialogue: 3,0:27:26.00,0:27:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Also, I run around a lot in my current job so that shouldn't be a problem at all.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:30.04,0:27:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}达拉尔女士，我真的很想知道
Dialogue: 3,0:27:30.04,0:27:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ms. Dalal, I really want to know this.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:32.36,0:27:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么你想从事一个没有女人从事的职业？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:32.36,0:27:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why do you want to take up a career in something where there are no women?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:37.92,0:27:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这很重要吗，先生？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:37.92,0:27:40.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Should that really matter, sir?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:40.84,0:27:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，让我们从大局出发
Dialogue: 3,0:27:40.84,0:27:42.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, let's look at the big picture.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:43.04,0:27:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们打破的成见越多，社会得到的益处就越多
Dialogue: 3,0:27:43.04,0:27:45.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The more stereotypes we break, the more society benefits.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:46.52,0:27:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我只想成为一名伟大的记者
Dialogue: 3,0:27:46.52,0:27:48.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I just want to be a great journalist.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:48.76,0:27:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回答你的问题，如果这能让我成为
Dialogue: 3,0:27:48.76,0:27:51.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And to answer your question, if that makes me...
Dialogue: 4,0:27:51.12,0:27:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}第一位女性金融记者
Dialogue: 3,0:27:51.12,0:27:53.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the first female financial journalist...
Dialogue: 4,0:27:53.40,0:27:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我就更应该努力工作，出类拔萃了
Dialogue: 3,0:27:53.40,0:27:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then it's all the more reason for me to work hard and excel.
Dialogue: 4,0:27:56.32,0:27:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，这是一条人迹罕至的道路
Dialogue: 3,0:27:56.32,0:27:58.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The fact that it's a lesser-travelled road...
Dialogue: 4,0:27:58.64,0:28:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不介意
Dialogue: 3,0:27:58.64,0:28:00.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that, that doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:00.80,0:28:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且，这也意味着较少的薪水
Dialogue: 3,0:28:00.80,0:28:04.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, lesser-travelled roads would also mean less salary.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:05.04,0:28:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们甚至不能支付你目前酒店工作收入的一半
Dialogue: 3,0:28:05.04,0:28:08.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can't even pay you half of what you are getting in your current hotel job.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:10.28,0:28:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我在金融部门工作..
Dialogue: 3,0:28:10.28,0:28:13.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, if I am working in the finance sector...
Dialogue: 4,0:28:13.56,0:28:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我至少需要足够的钱来管理我自己的财务
Dialogue: 3,0:28:13.56,0:28:17.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I will at least need enough to manage my own finances.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那要多少钱？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And, how much would that be?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:20.48,0:28:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯..
Dialogue: 3,0:28:20.48,0:28:21.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uhm...
Dialogue: 4,0:28:22.60,0:28:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们这些家伙怎么能泡出这么难喝的茶..
Dialogue: 3,0:28:22.60,0:28:24.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You guys make such pathetic tea...
Dialogue: 4,0:28:24.28,0:28:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}连饼干都对它不屑一顾
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.28,0:28:26.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that even the biscuit shies away.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:26.64,0:28:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你要上凉茶的话..
Dialogue: 3,0:28:26.64,0:28:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you are going to serve cold tea...
Dialogue: 4,0:28:29.12,0:28:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你为什么要把茶叶煮到焦？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:29.12,0:28:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then why do you boil the tea leaves till they burn?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:33.48,0:28:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这茶是谁泡的？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:33.48,0:28:34.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who makes this tea?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:34.92,0:28:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等一下，让我告诉你该怎么泡茶
Dialogue: 3,0:28:34.92,0:28:38.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wait a minute. Let me tell you how tea is made.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:38.88,0:28:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首先，烧水的时候不加茶叶
Dialogue: 3,0:28:38.88,0:28:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}First, boil some water without tea leaves.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:43.88,0:28:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}水开了之后加入一些豆蔻，生姜和罗邦戈
Dialogue: 3,0:28:43.88,0:28:51.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Add some cardamom, some ginger and some lobongo.
Dialogue: 4,0:28:52.00,0:28:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 那是什么?-丁香..
Dialogue: 3,0:28:52.00,0:28:56.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What's that? - Cloves...
Dialogue: 4,0:28:56.48,0:29:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 那就直接说丁香 -好的，主人，丁香
Dialogue: 3,0:28:56.48,0:29:00.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Then say that. - Okay, my master. Cloves.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:01.12,0:29:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}水开后，加入茶叶
Dialogue: 3,0:29:01.12,0:29:04.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once the water boils, add the tea leaves.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:04.12,0:29:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要把茶叶煮熟，好吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:29:04.12,0:29:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't boil the tea leaves to death. Okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:29:07.80,0:29:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后加一点牛奶，很简单，茶就好了
Dialogue: 3,0:29:07.80,0:29:10.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then add a little milk. Simple. Tea is ready.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:11.28,0:29:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么时候加糖?-最后
Dialogue: 3,0:29:11.28,0:29:13.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- And when do we add sugar? - At the end.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:15.04,0:29:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白了吗? 现在把这个给泡茶的人
Dialogue: 3,0:29:15.04,0:29:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you get it? Now give this to the one who makes tea.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:20.08,0:29:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你留着吧，先生，他不识字
Dialogue: 3,0:29:20.08,0:29:22.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Keep it with you, sir. He doesn't know to read.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:22.72,0:29:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会向他解释的
Dialogue: 3,0:29:22.72,0:29:23.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will explain it to him.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:23.96,0:29:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，带上这个！
Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.96,0:29:25.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello, take this with you!
Dialogue: 4,0:29:27.96,0:29:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 德巴什? -先生
Dialogue: 3,0:29:27.96,0:29:29.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Debashis? - Sir.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:30.08,0:29:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是苏切塔 · 达拉尔
Dialogue: 3,0:29:30.08,0:29:31.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is Sucheta Dalal.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:32.36,0:29:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生，你告诉过我
Dialogue: 3,0:29:32.36,0:29:33.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, yes, sir. You told me.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:34.12,0:29:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给她介绍下孟买证券交易所，好吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:29:34.12,0:29:36.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Show her the Bombay Stock Exchange, yeah?
Dialogue: 4,0:29:36.28,0:29:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:29:36.28,0:29:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure sir.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:37.56,0:29:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 一切顺利-谢谢，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:29:37.56,0:29:38.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- All the best. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:45.72,0:29:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的左边是印度国家银行
Dialogue: 3,0:29:45.72,0:29:46.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To your left, is the SBI.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:46.84,0:29:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们在那里存钱，然后在证交所赔钱
Dialogue: 3,0:29:46.84,0:29:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People save money there and lose it here at the BSE.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:53.84,0:29:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，我们到了
Dialogue: 3,0:29:53.84,0:29:55.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. Here we are.
Dialogue: 4,0:29:57.56,0:30:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便说一下，孟买最好的三明治在这里有卖
Dialogue: 3,0:29:57.56,0:30:00.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By the way, Bombay's best sandwiches are sold here.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:00.52,0:30:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}除此之外，还有免费的薄荷酱和市场八卦
Dialogue: 3,0:30:00.52,0:30:04.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And with that, mint chutney and market-gossip for free.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:04.28,0:30:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧
Dialogue: 3,0:30:04.28,0:30:05.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:06.80,0:30:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我们先去见阿加瓦尔先生，然后再去见其他人-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:30:06.80,0:30:10.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- First, we'll meet Agarwal sir and then the rest. - Okay.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:10.44,0:30:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 嘿！吉涅什 -德巴什
Dialogue: 3,0:30:10.44,0:30:12.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hey, Jignesh Bhai. - Debashis Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:13.80,0:30:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-兄弟，今天市场很震撼! -是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:13.80,0:30:15.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Debashis Bhai, the market is rocking today! - Is it?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:15.92,0:30:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}指数一路飙升，今天一定血赚
Dialogue: 3,0:30:15.92,0:30:18.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The index went through the roof of BSE. We will make a solid profit today.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:19.04,0:30:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看，在追求利润的过程中，别忘了你的报纸文章，Jignesh Bhai
Dialogue: 3,0:30:19.04,0:30:22.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, in the pursuit of profit, don't forget your newspaper article, Jignesh Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:22.68,0:30:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么时候能从苏拉特给我买到那些特别的糖果？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.68,0:30:25.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And when will you get me those special sweets from Surat?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:25.40,0:30:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要你一句话，老板
Dialogue: 3,0:30:25.40,0:30:26.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just say the word, boss.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:26.48,0:30:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我将乘早班火车去接他们
Dialogue: 3,0:30:26.48,0:30:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll call for them by the morning train.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:28.72,0:30:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 还需要什么吗?-不用了，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:30:28.72,0:30:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Anything else? - Please, thank you.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:30.20,0:30:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的再见-再见
Dialogue: 3,0:30:30.20,0:30:32.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay, then. Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:33.56,0:30:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是财经记者吉涅什
Dialogue: 3,0:30:33.56,0:30:36.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's the financial reporter of Ahmedabad Samachar. Jignesh.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:37.16,0:30:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了? 你在看什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:37.16,0:30:39.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What happened? What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:39.20,0:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，好的! 来吧
Dialogue: 3,0:30:39.20,0:30:40.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, okay! Come.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:40.92,0:30:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看，无论是记者还是财经类报纸... ... 都不可能在1200到1500卢比之间存活
Dialogue: 3,0:30:40.92,0:30:46.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, neither reporters nor financial newspapers... can survive at 1200 to 1500 rupees
Dialogue: 4,0:30:46.88,0:30:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是这个系统的工作原理
Dialogue: 3,0:30:46.88,0:30:48.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is how the system works.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:48.60,0:30:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们都和商人一起吃饭、睡觉、拉屎
Dialogue: 3,0:30:48.60,0:30:51.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They all eat, sleep and shit together with the traders.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:51.28,0:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们获得了如此多的内部消息，以至于在几年内，每个人都安定下来了
Dialogue: 3,0:30:51.28,0:30:54.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They get so much insider news that in a few years, everyone is well-settled.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:54.92,0:30:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你也炒股吗?-不... 我没有耐心
Dialogue: 3,0:30:54.92,0:30:57.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Do you trade too? - No... I don't have patience.
Dialogue: 4,0:30:57.16,0:31:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}炒股就像眼睁睁地看着油漆干枯或者草长出来
Dialogue: 3,0:30:57.16,0:31:00.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Trades are always like watching paint dry or grass grow.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:00.84,0:31:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我宁愿投资钻石
Dialogue: 3,0:31:00.84,0:31:03.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I would rather invest in diamonds.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:03.40,0:31:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，玩钻石的家伙在达拉尔街干什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:03.40,0:31:06.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what's a diamond guy doing in Dalal street?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:06.32,0:31:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我所有的消息来源都在这儿-啊
Dialogue: 3,0:31:06.32,0:31:08.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- All my sources are here. - Ah.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:08.08,0:31:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧
Dialogue: 3,0:31:08.08,0:31:08.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在Blowcast陷得太深了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We went too deep into Blowcast.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:14.12,0:31:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在正确的时间投入了正确的金额
Dialogue: 3,0:31:14.12,0:31:16.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We had invested the right amount at the right time.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:16.44,0:31:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}整个市场都在上涨，但我们完蛋了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:16.44,0:31:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The entire market is on a high. But we're screwed.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:18.96,0:31:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随它去吧，过去的就过去了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:18.96,0:31:20.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let it be. What's gone is gone.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:21.08,0:31:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，如果我们必须这么做，就不能完全靠自己
Dialogue: 3,0:31:21.08,0:31:25.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, if we have to do this, we can't do it by ourselves.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:25.76,0:31:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要员工，我们需要有经验的人
Dialogue: 3,0:31:25.76,0:31:29.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We need staff. We need someone who has some experience.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:29.32,0:31:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个知道怎么投资的人..
Dialogue: 3,0:31:29.32,0:31:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Someone who knows to play the ring...
Dialogue: 4,0:31:31.08,0:31:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能处理后勤和账务
Dialogue: 3,0:31:31.08,0:31:33.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and who can also handle the back office and accounts.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:34.12,0:31:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}总之，我们需要一个有团队精神的人，兄弟
Dialogue: 3,0:31:34.12,0:31:36.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In short, we need a team player, brother.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:40.92,0:31:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我认识一个这样的多面手
Dialogue: 3,0:31:40.92,0:31:42.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know one such all-rounder.
Dialogue: 4,0:31:44.40,0:31:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是嗑药了还是把我当傻瓜？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:44.40,0:31:47.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you on drugs or do you take me for a fool?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:48.16,0:31:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要我辞去安巴拉尔邦主的工作..
Dialogue: 3,0:31:48.16,0:31:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are asking me to quit my job with Ambalal saheb...
Dialogue: 4,0:31:50.56,0:31:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为你工作，薪水却更低？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:50.56,0:31:52.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and work for you at a lesser pay?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:53.44,0:31:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你喜欢为花生工作吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:53.44,0:31:55.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You enjoy working for peanuts?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:56.16,0:31:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别管薪水和佣金了，把精力集中在利润上
Dialogue: 3,0:31:56.16,0:31:58.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget salary and commission. Concentrate on the profit.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:03.72,0:32:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场是一口深井..
Dialogue: 3,0:32:03.72,0:32:05.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The share market is a deep well...
Dialogue: 4,0:32:05.88,0:32:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以满足整个国家对金钱的渴望
Dialogue: 3,0:32:05.88,0:32:08.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that can quench the entire nation's thirst for money.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:09.52,0:32:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想跳进这口井里
Dialogue: 3,0:32:09.52,0:32:11.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I want to dive into this well.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:12.68,0:32:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想深入研究
Dialogue: 3,0:32:12.68,0:32:14.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to go very deep.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:17.36,0:32:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我想创造历史
Dialogue: 3,0:32:17.36,0:32:19.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I want to create history.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:19.80,0:32:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}历史并不容易创造，它需要人们的信念和支持
Dialogue: 3,0:32:19.80,0:32:23.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And history is not easy to make. It needs the conviction and support of people.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:24.72,0:32:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想建立一支100人的军队... ... 他们愿意为我付出100% 的努力
Dialogue: 3,0:32:24.72,0:32:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to build an army of a 100... who are willing to give me their 100 percent.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:30.08,0:32:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么我百分之一千零一肯定，我们能够创造历史
Dialogue: 3,0:32:30.08,0:32:32.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then I'm a thousand and one per cent sure that we'll create history.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:35.72,0:32:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的军队只能有一个指挥官，布尚·巴特
Dialogue: 3,0:32:35.72,0:32:38.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There can only be one commander to my army. Bhushan Bhatt.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:41.52,0:32:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是老搭档了
Dialogue: 3,0:32:41.52,0:32:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are old partners.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:43.64,0:32:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是想让我做合伙人吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:32:43.64,0:32:45.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you offering me a partnership?
Dialogue: 4,0:32:45.28,0:32:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想要什么就拿什么，公司是你的了
Dialogue: 3,0:32:45.28,0:32:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Take whatever you want. The company is yours.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:47.44,0:32:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但首先，请接受我的提议，与我携起手来
Dialogue: 3,0:32:47.44,0:32:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But first, accept my offer and join hands with me.
Dialogue: 4,0:32:58.56,0:33:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏切塔]“当我忙于了解股票市场的世界时... ... ”
Dialogue: 3,0:32:58.56,0:33:01.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'While I was busy understanding the world of the share market...'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:01.72,0:33:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 哈沙德正忙着让股票市场成为他的世界”
Dialogue: 3,0:33:01.72,0:33:04.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...Harshad was busy making the share market his world.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:07.56,0:33:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在玩这个游戏，而我还在学
Dialogue: 3,0:33:07.56,0:33:10.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'He was playing the game, I was still learning it.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:10.76,0:33:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}慢慢地，他的视野开始开阔起来
Dialogue: 3,0:33:10.76,0:33:13.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Slowly but surely, his horizons began to widen.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:13.92,0:33:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，不仅仅是一场比赛，他看到了整个比赛场地
Dialogue: 3,0:33:13.92,0:33:17.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Now, more than just one game, he was looking at the whole playing field.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:18.04,0:33:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快，他的梦想就会超越这枚戒指
Dialogue: 3,0:33:18.04,0:33:23.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Soon, his dreams would outgrow the ring.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:25.36,0:33:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是在这个圈子里，有一个领袖，黑眼镜蛇，也就是马努·蒙德拉
Dialogue: 3,0:33:25.36,0:33:30.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But in this ring, there was a ringmaster. Black Cobra. That is, Manu Mundra.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:33.72,0:33:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场随着马努的曲调起舞
Dialogue: 3,0:33:33.72,0:33:36.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The market danced to Manu Bhai's tunes.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:37.28,0:33:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使是印度最大的公司也担心蒙德拉的决定
Dialogue: 3,0:33:37.28,0:33:41.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Even the biggest companies in India feared Mundra's decisions.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:43.16,0:33:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在市场上有一只
Dialogue: 3,0:33:43.16,0:33:45.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And in the market, there was one mongoose...
Dialogue: 4,0:33:46.08,0:33:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能对付眼镜蛇的猫鼬
Dialogue: 3,0:33:46.08,0:33:48.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who could take on the cobra.'
Dialogue: 4,0:33:51.16,0:33:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，我会的，好的
Dialogue: 3,0:33:51.16,0:33:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, I'll do it. Okay.
Dialogue: 4,0:33:55.84,0:33:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，是吉尼斯打来的
Dialogue: 3,0:33:55.84,0:33:58.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, it was Jignesh on the phone.
Dialogue: 4,0:33:58.64,0:34:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个经纪人的会员卡正在被拍卖，你怎么看？
Dialogue: 3,0:33:58.64,0:34:01.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A broker's membership card is being auctioned. What do you say?
Dialogue: 4,0:34:02.44,0:34:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么好说的，你说吧
Dialogue: 3,0:34:02.44,0:34:03.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's there to say. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:03.96,0:34:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我已经向帕里克寻求赞助了
Dialogue: 3,0:34:03.96,0:34:06.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've already spoken to Parekh Bhai for sponsorship.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:06.80,0:34:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 钱会安排好的-很好
Dialogue: 3,0:34:06.80,0:34:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- The money will be arranged. - Good.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:11.24,0:34:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}茶
Dialogue: 3,0:34:11.24,0:34:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tea.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:12.64,0:34:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}克萨里旅游公司的人打电话来了
Dialogue: 3,0:34:12.64,0:34:14.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The people from Kesari Tours had called.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:14.96,0:34:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们十二月份去西姆拉吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:34:14.96,0:34:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's go to Shimla in December?
Dialogue: 4,0:34:17.00,0:34:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你听到妈妈说什么了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:34:17.00,0:34:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Did you hear what mummy said?
Dialogue: 4,0:34:18.84,0:34:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她想在12月份去西姆拉
Dialogue: 3,0:34:18.84,0:34:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}She wants to go to Shimla in December.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:20.72,0:34:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉她，她会冻僵的！
Dialogue: 3,0:34:20.72,0:34:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell her she will freeze!
Dialogue: 4,0:34:23.76,0:34:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}十二月份人们从四面八方赶来看雪
Dialogue: 3,0:34:23.76,0:34:27.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Duffer, in December people come from all over to see the snowfall.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:27.52,0:34:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 十二月是个好时机-是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:34:27.52,0:34:29.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- December is the right time. - Right?
Dialogue: 4,0:34:29.20,0:34:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是啊-价格也很合理
Dialogue: 3,0:34:29.20,0:34:30.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yeah. - Even the cost is reasonable.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:30.88,0:34:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们还有一个素食厨师，所以我们可以吃古吉拉特食物
Dialogue: 3,0:34:30.88,0:34:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And they also have a vegetarian cook. So, we can have Gujarati food.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:33.72,0:34:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了，那我们一路上都吃虾肉
Dialogue: 3,0:34:33.72,0:34:36.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's great. Then we'll have Shrikhand-Poori all the way.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:37.08,0:34:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他们把细节发过来
Dialogue: 3,0:34:37.08,0:34:38.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ask them to send the details.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:40.92,0:34:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去吧，打开收音机，该听爸爸的新闻了，去吧
Dialogue: 3,0:34:40.92,0:34:43.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go, turn on the radio. It's time for Pappa's news. Go.
Dialogue: 4,0:34:53.32,0:34:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 这个令人悲伤的消息，英迪拉 · 甘地总理去世了”
Dialogue: 3,0:34:53.32,0:34:57.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Newsreader] '...this sad news. Prime Minister Indira Gandhi is no more.'
Dialogue: 4,0:34:57.08,0:34:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}甘地夫人被她的保安枪击
Dialogue: 3,0:34:57.08,0:34:59.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Mrs. Gandhi was critically injured this morning...'
Dialogue: 4,0:34:59.88,0:35:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}于今天早上受了重伤
Dialogue: 3,0:34:59.88,0:35:02.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...after being shot by her security guards.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:02.52,0:35:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她立即被送往全印度医学科学研究所
Dialogue: 3,0:35:02.52,0:35:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'She was immediately rushed to the All India Institute of Medical Sciences...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:05.80,0:35:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但因伤势过重去世
Dialogue: 3,0:35:05.80,0:35:07.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...where she succumbed to her injuries.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:07.80,0:35:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}据可靠消息称..
Dialogue: 3,0:35:07.80,0:35:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'According to reliable sources...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:10.16,0:35:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“拉吉夫 · 甘地将宣誓就任下一任印度总理”
Dialogue: 3,0:35:10.16,0:35:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...Rajiv Gandhi will be sworn in as the next Prime Minister of India.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:12.48,0:35:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有人试图在总理府
Dialogue: 3,0:35:12.48,0:35:14.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There was an attempt...
Dialogue: 4,0:35:14.04,0:35:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刺杀甘地夫人
Dialogue: 3,0:35:14.04,0:35:16.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...on Mrs. Gandhi life at the Prime Minister's residence.
Dialogue: 4,0:35:16.84,0:35:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她立即被送往全印度医学科学研究所
Dialogue: 3,0:35:16.84,0:35:19.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}She was taken to All India Institute of Medical Sciences immediately.
Dialogue: 4,0:35:19.32,0:35:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}英迪拉 · 甘地总理之死
Dialogue: 3,0:35:19.32,0:35:21.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Death of the Prime Minister Indira Gandhi...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:21.76,0:35:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 是印度政治的一个分水岭”
Dialogue: 3,0:35:21.76,0:35:24.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] '...was a watershed event in Indian politics.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:24.08,0:35:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“这是意想不到的，令人震惊的... ... ”
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.08,0:35:26.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'It was unexpected and shocking...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:26.24,0:35:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“它产生了强烈的反响... ... ”
Dialogue: 3,0:35:26.24,0:35:28.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'and it had violent repercussions...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:28.20,0:35:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一方面，成千上万的人死于暴乱... ..
Dialogue: 3,0:35:28.20,0:35:31.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'On one hand, thousands of people were dying in riots...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:31.04,0:35:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}另一方面，整个国家对此视而不见
Dialogue: 3,0:35:31.04,0:35:34.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...and on the other, the nation turned a blind eye to the situation.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:34.76,0:35:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与此同时，拉吉夫•甘地(Rajiv Gandhi)正在被推举为总理
Dialogue: 3,0:35:34.76,0:35:39.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Meanwhile, Rajiv Gandhi was being served up Prime Ministership on a platter...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:39.36,0:35:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多人不相信一个作为飞行员的男人..
Dialogue: 3,0:35:39.36,0:35:44.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And many people refused to believe that a man who was just a pilot...'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:44.48,0:35:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“仅仅因为他的姓氏是甘地，就有能力领导这个国家”
Dialogue: 3,0:35:44.48,0:35:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...would be able to lead the country just because his surname was Gandhi.'
Dialogue: 4,0:35:48.08,0:35:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个飞行员能飞多久? 你觉得怎么样，马赫什瓦里？
Dialogue: 3,0:35:48.08,0:35:50.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How long will this pilot last? What do you think, Maheshwari?
Dialogue: 4,0:35:51.60,0:35:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最多到12月
Dialogue: 3,0:35:51.60,0:35:53.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Till December at best.
Dialogue: 4,0:35:53.72,0:35:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}选举之后就没他的事了
Dialogue: 3,0:35:53.72,0:35:55.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He won't be there beyond the elections.
Dialogue: 4,0:35:57.32,0:36:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们不相信这架飞机会起飞
Dialogue: 3,0:35:57.32,0:36:00.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People don't believe that this pilot will take off.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:02.28,0:36:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我认为时机已经成熟..
Dialogue: 3,0:36:02.28,0:36:04.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I think the time is ripe...
Dialogue: 4,0:36:06.48,0:36:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}解决所有的牛市交易
Dialogue: 3,0:36:06.48,0:36:09.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to square off all the bull trades...
Dialogue: 4,0:36:11.12,0:36:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}并在市场上占有一席之地
Dialogue: 3,0:36:11.12,0:36:12.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and take positions in the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:14.40,0:36:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们改写游戏规则
Dialogue: 3,0:36:14.40,0:36:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's f*****g break the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:19.64,0:36:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阿什温，尽你所能从市场上撤出来
Dialogue: 3,0:36:19.64,0:36:23.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai Ashwin, pull out all you can from the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:24.00,0:36:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个灾难性下跌
Dialogue: 3,0:36:24.00,0:36:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a nosedive.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:27.08,0:36:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快指数就会落入尘埃
Dialogue: 3,0:36:27.08,0:36:30.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Soon the index will be in the dust.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:30.32,0:36:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们先让它恢复一点，然后再卖掉
Dialogue: 3,0:36:30.32,0:36:33.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's allow it to recover a little. Then we'll sell.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:34.08,0:36:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你怎么说，哈沙德?-‘你怎么想? ’
Dialogue: 3,0:36:34.08,0:36:35.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What do you say, Harshad? -[Pranav] 'What do you think?'
Dialogue: 4,0:36:36.32,0:36:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是经济舱的飞机
Dialogue: 3,0:36:36.32,0:36:38.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is not the economy class of an airplane.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:38.56,0:36:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}国家的经济现在掌握在他的手中
Dialogue: 3,0:36:38.56,0:36:40.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The nation's economy is in his hands now.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:40.80,0:36:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快，我们就会拿着乞讨用的碗在街上游荡
Dialogue: 3,0:36:40.80,0:36:43.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And soon, we will be roaming the market with begging bowls.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:44.56,0:36:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德，你有在听吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:36:44.56,0:36:46.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 4,0:36:46.68,0:36:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我说了，你会头疼的
Dialogue: 3,0:36:46.68,0:36:49.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I say what I want, you'll get a headache.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:49.96,0:36:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 还想听吗?-好吧
Dialogue: 3,0:36:49.96,0:36:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Still want to hear it? - Okay.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:52.04,0:36:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我洗耳恭听
Dialogue: 3,0:36:52.04,0:36:54.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:56.36,0:36:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上的马萨拉是用四种香料制成的
Dialogue: 3,0:36:56.36,0:36:58.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The masala of the market is created from four spices.
Dialogue: 4,0:36:58.96,0:37:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 马萨拉?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:36:58.96,0:37:00.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Masala? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:00.96,0:37:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}首先，情报，或者信息，内幕交易，研究
Dialogue: 3,0:37:00.96,0:37:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Firstly, tip. Or information, insider trading, research.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:05.16,0:37:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在给它增加一些风险
Dialogue: 3,0:37:05.16,0:37:06.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now add some risk to it.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:06.88,0:37:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风险越高，市场越刺激
Dialogue: 3,0:37:06.88,0:37:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Higher the risk, spicier the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:10.40,0:37:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这个混合物里加入一些情绪
Dialogue: 3,0:37:10.40,0:37:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Grind some passion into this mixture.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:12.96,0:37:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么样的情绪?-激情
Dialogue: 3,0:37:12.96,0:37:14.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What kind of passion? -[Harshad] 'Emotion.'
Dialogue: 4,0:37:15.36,0:37:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正如交易专家所言，“理解市场情绪”
Dialogue: 3,0:37:15.36,0:37:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As the trade pundits say, "Understand the sentiment of the market".
Dialogue: 4,0:37:18.72,0:37:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，理解这种情绪
Dialogue: 3,0:37:18.72,0:37:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, understand the emotion.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:21.36,0:37:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在再加上一点运气，就是这样，市场上的马萨拉已经准备好了
Dialogue: 3,0:37:21.36,0:37:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now add a pinch of luck. There you go. The market's masala is ready.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:25.40,0:37:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是做生意还是做饭? 阿什温？
Dialogue: 3,0:37:25.40,0:37:27.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is he trading or cooking? Ashwin?
Dialogue: 4,0:37:27.92,0:37:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉纳夫，你的马萨拉太情绪化了
Dialogue: 3,0:37:27.92,0:37:30.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav Bhai, your masala is too heavy on emotions.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:30.80,0:37:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人在情绪化的时候总是会犯错误
Dialogue: 3,0:37:30.80,0:37:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And man always makes mistakes when he is emotional.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:33.72,0:37:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是增加风险缓和的时候了
Dialogue: 3,0:37:33.72,0:37:36.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the time to add a tempering of risk.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:36.28,0:37:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在不是卖的时候，是买的时候
Dialogue: 3,0:37:36.28,0:37:38.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is not the time to sell. It's the time to buy.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:38.76,0:37:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些熊市对市场的拉动力越小..
Dialogue: 3,0:37:38.76,0:37:40.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The lower these bears pull the market...
Dialogue: 4,0:37:41.40,0:37:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它就会反弹得越高
Dialogue: 3,0:37:41.40,0:37:42.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the higher it will bounce.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:42.92,0:37:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一定会反弹的，看看这个
Dialogue: 3,0:37:42.92,0:37:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It will rebound. Look at this.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:46.96,0:37:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个飞行员要飞得很高，我们也是
Dialogue: 3,0:37:46.96,0:37:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This pilot is going to fly high. And so are we.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:50.96,0:37:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉纳夫兄弟，我很少同意哈尔沙德的观点
Dialogue: 3,0:37:50.96,0:37:54.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav Bhai, I rarely agree with Harshad.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:56.64,0:37:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但今天我同意
Dialogue: 3,0:37:56.64,0:37:58.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But today is one such day.
Dialogue: 4,0:37:59.36,0:38:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是你们的问题所在
Dialogue: 3,0:37:59.36,0:38:01.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is exactly the problem with you Bulls.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:01.88,0:38:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公牛用希望杀死你
Dialogue: 3,0:38:01.88,0:38:04.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A Bull kills you with hope.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:04.60,0:38:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}熊用恐惧杀死你
Dialogue: 3,0:38:04.60,0:38:06.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And a Bear kills you with fear.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:10.52,0:38:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看这个，读这个段落，看
Dialogue: 3,0:38:10.52,0:38:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at this. Read this paragraph. Look.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:14.88,0:38:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印地罗，Zuari Agro，SPIC
Dialogue: 3,0:38:14.88,0:38:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Indrol, Zuari Agro, SPIC.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:18.04,0:38:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道它们有多便宜吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:38:18.04,0:38:19.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know how cheap they are?
Dialogue: 4,0:38:19.76,0:38:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦它们激增，就没有什么能够阻挡
Dialogue: 3,0:38:19.76,0:38:22.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once they surge, there will be no stopping them.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:22.36,0:38:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你疯了吗? 这个国家正在燃烧
Dialogue: 3,0:38:22.36,0:38:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you crazy? The country is up in flames.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:25.64,0:38:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们不是在开车，而是在焚烧汽车
Dialogue: 3,0:38:25.64,0:38:27.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People aren't driving cars. They're burning them.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:28.04,0:38:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这样的时刻，你想投资石油，石油？
Dialogue: 3,0:38:28.04,0:38:30.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And at a time like this, you want to invest in oil, in petroleum?
Dialogue: 4,0:38:31.12,0:38:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的朋友，不管怎样你都需要汽油，不管是开车还是烧车
Dialogue: 3,0:38:31.12,0:38:35.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My friend. You need petrol either way. Whether it is to drive a car, or to burn it.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:37.72,0:38:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别管情感价值了，看看真正的价值吧，亲爱的
Dialogue: 3,0:38:37.72,0:38:40.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget the sentimental value. Look at the real value, darling.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:49.64,0:38:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，这是确认的消息，英卓尔今天会跌到谷底
Dialogue: 3,0:38:49.64,0:38:52.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, brother. This is confirmed news. Indrol will drown today.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:52.88,0:38:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁在耍英卓尔？
Dialogue: 3,0:38:52.88,0:38:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who's screwing with Indrol?
Dialogue: 4,0:38:54.44,0:38:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}眼镜蛇! 眼镜蛇！
Dialogue: 3,0:38:54.44,0:38:55.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Cobra! Cobra!
Dialogue: 4,0:38:56.08,0:38:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他做空英卓尔，今天肯定会崩溃
Dialogue: 3,0:38:56.08,0:38:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's short on Indrol. It will crash today for sure.
Dialogue: 4,0:38:59.16,0:39:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我们已经在这个事情上做了很长时间的准备
Dialogue: 3,0:38:59.16,0:39:00.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we've taken a rather long position on it.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:01.04,0:39:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样，兄弟? 眼镜蛇的尾巴更长
Dialogue: 3,0:39:01.04,0:39:05.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So what, brother? The Cobra's tail is longer.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:05.68,0:39:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Bhushan ]‘相信我，收手吧，我们能承受一点损失’
Dialogue: 3,0:39:05.68,0:39:08.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'Trust me, let it go, we can bear a little loss.'
Dialogue: 4,0:39:08.24,0:39:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们没有足够的资金来持有头寸
Dialogue: 3,0:39:08.24,0:39:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we don't have the cash to hold our position.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:11.64,0:39:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们要抓住这条该死的眼镜蛇的长尾巴！
Dialogue: 3,0:39:11.64,0:39:13.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll catch this bloody Cobra by his long tail!
Dialogue: 4,0:39:14.12,0:39:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会离开很长一段时间
Dialogue: 3,0:39:14.12,0:39:15.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He'll be gone for a long time.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:16.04,0:39:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 让我们所有的客户都买入-什么? ！
Dialogue: 3,0:39:16.04,0:39:18.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Let's ask all our clients to buy instead. -Huh?!
Dialogue: 4,0:39:21.08,0:39:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我们所有的客户购买英卓尔，尽可能多的购买
Dialogue: 3,0:39:21.08,0:39:25.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell all our clients to buy Indrol. Buy as much as possible. Everything.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:25.48,0:39:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都买一点，尽可能多买一点
Dialogue: 3,0:39:25.48,0:39:28.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Buy Indrol, everyone. Buy as much as possible.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:30.40,0:39:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 嘿，萨钦兄弟...-你好，悉达基，最近怎么样？
Dialogue: 3,0:39:30.40,0:39:33.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hey, Sachin Bhau... - Hello, Siddeshji. How're you?
Dialogue: 4,0:39:33.64,0:39:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有好消息要告诉你，瓦吉大哥，玩得开心吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:39:33.64,0:39:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have good news for you. Vaghji Bhai, having fun?
Dialogue: 4,0:39:36.56,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，维克多 · 安娜，你好吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:39:36.56,0:39:38.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello, Victor Anna. How're you?
Dialogue: 4,0:39:38.52,0:39:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，阿南德·库玛吉，最近怎样？
Dialogue: 3,0:39:38.52,0:39:40.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Greetings, Anand Kumarji. How're you doing?
Dialogue: 4,0:39:41.08,0:39:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉希尔，怎么了? 今天是投资的好日子
Dialogue: 3,0:39:41.08,0:39:44.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rahil, what's up? It's a great day for investment.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:44.24,0:39:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天就买下所有的股票
Dialogue: 3,0:39:44.24,0:39:45.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Buy all the shares today.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:45.88,0:39:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是保证利润的时候了
Dialogue: 3,0:39:45.88,0:39:47.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the time for a guaranteed profit.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:47.80,0:39:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 我向你保证
Dialogue: 3,0:39:47.80,0:39:49.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... I guarantee you.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:49.60,0:39:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天是投资的好日子，相信我
Dialogue: 3,0:39:49.60,0:39:52.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is a good day to invest. Trust me.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:52.48,0:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了
Dialogue: 3,0:39:52.48,0:39:53.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's great.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:53.80,0:39:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是哈沙德的保证，别担心
Dialogue: 3,0:39:53.80,0:39:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's Harshad's guarantee. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 4,0:39:57.08,0:39:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你想投资一大笔钱，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:39:57.08,0:39:58.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You wanted to invest a big amount, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:39:58.88,0:40:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧，多投一些！
Dialogue: 3,0:39:58.88,0:40:00.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on, spend some more!
Dialogue: 4,0:40:00.16,0:40:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是收购股份的大好机会
Dialogue: 3,0:40:00.16,0:40:02.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a great opportunity to sweep up these shares.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:02.32,0:40:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最顺利的时候，这些股票会让你变得富有
Dialogue: 3,0:40:02.32,0:40:04.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the smoothest time. This share will make you rich.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:04.96,0:40:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你同意的话，这次我们可以给他沉重打击
Dialogue: 3,0:40:04.96,0:40:07.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you agree, we can hit a sixer on this one.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:07.84,0:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:40:07.84,0:40:09.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:09.84,0:40:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:40:09.84,0:40:10.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What?
Dialogue: 4,0:40:11.80,0:40:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:40:11.80,0:40:14.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure. Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:23.48,0:40:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我很高兴我们今天早上卖掉了英卓尔
Dialogue: 3,0:40:23.48,0:40:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm glad we sold off Indrol this morning.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:26.20,0:40:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是不是应该平仓了？
Dialogue: 3,0:40:26.20,0:40:28.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Shall we square off the positions and book our profit?
Dialogue: 4,0:40:28.56,0:40:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你觉得呢?-不，让我们保持这个位置
Dialogue: 3,0:40:28.56,0:40:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What say, Raju? - No. Let's hold the position.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:30.96,0:40:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还会继续跌
Dialogue: 3,0:40:30.96,0:40:32.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Indrol will drop further.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:44.16,0:40:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，过来
Dialogue: 3,0:40:44.16,0:40:45.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen, come here.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:47.72,0:40:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}买入英卓尔的股票，告诉所有人
Dialogue: 3,0:40:47.72,0:40:49.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Buy Indrol. Tell everyone.
Dialogue: 4,0:40:52.52,0:40:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}英卓尔! 英卓尔! 英卓尔！
Dialogue: 3,0:40:52.52,0:40:55.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Indrol! Indrol! Indrol!
Dialogue: 4,0:41:45.20,0:41:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我得去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 3,0:41:45.20,0:41:47.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've to go to the washroom.
Dialogue: 4,0:41:57.04,0:42:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为了坚守阵地，我们遭受了严重的损失
Dialogue: 3,0:41:57.04,0:42:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In trying to hold our positions, we've incurred a serious loss.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:00.56,0:42:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们都准备好了
Dialogue: 3,0:42:00.56,0:42:02.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We were all set.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:02.48,0:42:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}突然，就在空头回补开始的时候..
Dialogue: 3,0:42:02.48,0:42:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[phone rings] - Suddenly, just as short covering began...
Dialogue: 4,0:42:04.56,0:42:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股价涨起来了
Dialogue: 3,0:42:04.56,0:42:05.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...it started rising.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:06.12,0:42:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等一下，什么事？
Dialogue: 3,0:42:06.12,0:42:08.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}One minute. Yes?
Dialogue: 4,0:42:09.12,0:42:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再见
Dialogue: 3,0:42:09.12,0:42:10.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Later.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:10.64,0:42:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁在抬高股价？
Dialogue: 3,0:42:10.64,0:42:11.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who's pushing it up?
Dialogue: 4,0:42:11.92,0:42:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在最后一刻，买单..
Dialogue: 3,0:42:11.92,0:42:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai, at the last moment, the buying orders...
Dialogue: 4,0:42:13.08,0:42:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉朱! 别像个混蛋一样说话
Dialogue: 3,0:42:13.08,0:42:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Raju! Don't talk like an ass.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:16.96,0:42:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是谁在买入? LIC? UTI? 安巴尼？
Dialogue: 3,0:42:16.96,0:42:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where are the buying orders coming from? LIC? UTI? Ambani?
Dialogue: 4,0:42:20.64,0:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 谁买的?-我们不能肯定
Dialogue: 3,0:42:20.64,0:42:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Who's buying it? - We can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:23.00,0:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是那个哈尔沙德... 他心情很好，买了很多股票
Dialogue: 3,0:42:23.00,0:42:26.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But that Harshad... he was in good mood. He's buying a lot nowadays.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:27.80,0:42:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德? 谁? 那个该死的哈尔沙德・梅塔？
Dialogue: 3,0:42:27.80,0:42:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad? Who? That f****r Harshad Mehta?
Dialogue: 4,0:42:31.24,0:42:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 3,0:42:31.24,0:42:32.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Manu Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:32.68,0:42:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他给他的投资者60% 到70% 的回报
Dialogue: 3,0:42:32.68,0:42:36.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's giving 60 to 70 percent returns to his investors.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:37.04,0:42:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 谁在资助他?-不只是一个投资人
Dialogue: 3,0:42:37.04,0:42:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- And who's funding him? - It isn't just one source.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:40.08,0:42:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们都是真正的投资者
Dialogue: 3,0:42:40.08,0:42:41.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They're all are genuine investors.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:41.76,0:42:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿，马赫什瓦里..
Dialogue: 3,0:42:41.76,0:42:43.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hey, Maheshwari...
Dialogue: 4,0:42:43.76,0:42:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[电话铃声]
Dialogue: 3,0:42:43.76,0:42:44.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 4,0:42:46.40,0:42:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“稍等一会儿”
Dialogue: 3,0:42:46.40,0:42:48.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Manu Manek] 'Hold on for a minute.'
Dialogue: 4,0:42:49.08,0:42:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在我们这个市场上，没有真正的投资者..
Dialogue: 3,0:42:49.08,0:42:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In this market of ours, there are no genuine investors...
Dialogue: 4,0:42:52.36,0:42:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都是机会主义者
Dialogue: 3,0:42:52.36,0:42:53.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Everyone is an opportunist.
Dialogue: 4,0:42:54.88,0:42:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说的那个混蛋... 他叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 3,0:42:54.88,0:42:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that a*****e you are talking about... what's his name?
Dialogue: 4,0:42:58.20,0:42:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哈尔沙德 · 梅塔-哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 3,0:42:58.20,0:42:59.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad Mehta. -[Manu] 'Harshad Mehta.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:00.12,0:43:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时机成熟时，我要确保他也倒下
Dialogue: 3,0:43:00.12,0:43:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When the time comes, we'll make sure he falls too.
Dialogue: 4,0:43:07.08,0:43:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家好
Dialogue: 3,0:43:07.08,0:43:08.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Newsreader] 'Greetings.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:08.12,0:43:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度财政部长维什瓦纳特•普拉塔普•辛格今天向议会提交了年度预算
Dialogue: 3,0:43:08.12,0:43:12.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}' Finance Minister, Mr. Vishwanath Pratap Singh presented the annual budget in the parliament today.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:12.72,0:43:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其中最精彩的部分是
Dialogue: 3,0:43:12.72,0:43:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The highlights of which, are thus.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:14.44,0:43:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“在16个月的时间里，哈沙德买下了他能买到的一切... ... ”
Dialogue: 3,0:43:14.44,0:43:16.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'For 16 months, Harshad bought all he could...'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:16.96,0:43:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 没有任何后备计划
Dialogue: 3,0:43:16.96,0:43:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...without any backup plan.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:18.28,0:43:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他对 Indrol、 Zuari Agro 和 SPIC 等公司进行了大量投资
Dialogue: 3,0:43:18.28,0:43:22.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...he invested heavily in companies like Indrol, Zuari Agro and SPIC.
Dialogue: 4,0:43:22.52,0:43:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“公牛相信正在进行的自由化政策，并以此为先”
Dialogue: 3,0:43:22.52,0:43:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The Bull set his pace trusting the on-going liberalisation policy.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:26.76,0:43:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是政府对长期财政政策的承诺..
Dialogue: 3,0:43:26.76,0:43:31.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'but the promises that the government had made on long-term fiscal policies...'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:31.28,0:43:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 已经被预算所遗忘”
Dialogue: 3,0:43:31.28,0:43:33.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...had been forgotten in this budget.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:33.60,0:43:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}财政部长表示，在所有收入计算之后... ..
Dialogue: 3,0:43:33.60,0:43:35.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The finance minister said that after all revenue calculations...
Dialogue: 4,0:43:35.96,0:43:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 明年的预算将赤字365亿卢比..
Dialogue: 3,0:43:35.96,0:43:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...next year's budget will be short by 3,650 crore rupees...
Dialogue: 4,0:43:40.36,0:43:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对于这个赤字还没有任何安排
Dialogue: 3,0:43:40.36,0:43:43.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and for this deficit there is no arrangement yet.
Dialogue: 4,0:43:43.12,0:43:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}恐惧总是压倒希望
Dialogue: 3,0:43:43.12,0:43:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Fear always overpowers hope.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:45.20,0:43:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“熊帮正是利用这种情绪来对抗牛市”
Dialogue: 3,0:43:45.20,0:43:48.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And the bear gang was using this sentiment against the Bull.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:48.60,0:43:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“牛削弱的那一刻，熊就强势起来了”
Dialogue: 3,0:43:48.60,0:43:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The moment the Bull weakened, the Bears rose.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:51.16,0:43:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一次，马努攻击了哈尔沙德最喜欢的一只股票
Dialogue: 3,0:43:51.16,0:43:55.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And this time Manu Mundra attacked one of Harshad's favourite stocks.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:55.12,0:43:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SPIC
Dialogue: 3,0:43:55.12,0:43:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'SPIC.'
Dialogue: 4,0:43:59.48,0:44:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SPIC 是哈尔沙德的心脏所在
Dialogue: 3,0:43:59.48,0:44:02.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SPIC is where Harshad's heart is.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:02.76,0:44:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们应该进一步拉低 SPIC
Dialogue: 3,0:44:02.76,0:44:04.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we must pull SPIC down some more.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:05.16,0:44:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SPIC指数进一步下跌，哈尔萨德的指数就会下跌
Dialogue: 3,0:44:05.16,0:44:08.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The further SPIC falls, the lower Harshad drops.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:08.96,0:44:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是谁？
Dialogue: 3,0:44:08.96,0:44:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who the f**k is this Harshad Mehta?
Dialogue: 4,0:44:11.92,0:44:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是塔塔家的人吗? 他是安巴尼家的人吗? 他是谁？
Dialogue: 3,0:44:11.92,0:44:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is he a Tata? Is he an Ambani? Who's he?
Dialogue: 4,0:44:15.20,0:44:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马赫什瓦里..
Dialogue: 3,0:44:15.20,0:44:16.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maheshwari...
Dialogue: 4,0:44:16.92,0:44:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}攻击股票只会... 啊啊啊！烫死我了
Dialogue: 3,0:44:16.92,0:44:19.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...targeting the stock will only... M**********r!
Dialogue: 4,0:44:21.44,0:44:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}普拉蒙德? 你为什么用钢杯给我倒茶？
Dialogue: 3,0:44:21.44,0:44:24.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pramod? Why did you get me tea in a steel cup?
Dialogue: 4,0:44:26.72,0:44:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的天啊！
Dialogue: 3,0:44:26.72,0:44:28.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}M**********r!
Dialogue: 4,0:44:30.44,0:44:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}攻击股票只会动摇他，而不会击垮他
Dialogue: 3,0:44:30.44,0:44:35.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Targeting the stock will only shake him, not break him.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:36.20,0:44:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他可能会停顿一下，但他不会屈服
Dialogue: 3,0:44:36.20,0:44:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He might pause. But he won't bend.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:39.88,0:44:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果有什么是应该攻击的... 不是股票，而是他的名声
Dialogue: 3,0:44:39.88,0:44:42.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If there's one thing we want to target... It's not the stock. It's his reputation.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:44.64,0:44:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马赫什瓦里，当你不能玷污别人的作品时，那就玷污他们的名声
Dialogue: 3,0:44:44.64,0:44:49.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maheshwari, when you can't tarnish someone's work, tarnish their name.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:50.80,0:44:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的名声越坏，人们就越不信任他
Dialogue: 3,0:44:50.80,0:44:54.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The worse his reputation, The lesser people will trust him.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:55.24,0:44:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有信任，就不会有任何投资
Dialogue: 3,0:44:55.24,0:44:57.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And without trust, there won't be any investment.
Dialogue: 4,0:44:57.88,0:45:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果没有投资，可以想象一下牛被阉割是什么样
Dialogue: 3,0:44:57.88,0:45:02.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without investment, Consider the bull's balls cut forever.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:03.44,0:45:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就废了
Dialogue: 3,0:45:03.44,0:45:04.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It'll never rise again.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:07.68,0:45:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么我们这样……
Dialogue: 3,0:45:07.68,0:45:09.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So let's do one thing.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:09.60,0:45:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在他的投资者中建立一种对哈尔萨德的观点
Dialogue: 3,0:45:09.60,0:45:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's create a perception about Harshad among his investors.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:12.56,0:45:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么观点？
Dialogue: 3,0:45:12.56,0:45:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What perception?
Dialogue: 4,0:45:13.68,0:45:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德在 SPIC 损失了六七百万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:45:13.68,0:45:16.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That Harshad has lost 60-70 lakhs in SPIC.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:16.32,0:45:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不... 不止这些
Dialogue: 3,0:45:16.32,0:45:18.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No... More than one crore.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:20.48,0:45:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个数字一定要很大
Dialogue: 3,0:45:20.48,0:45:22.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The number must be huge.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:23.24,0:45:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}到那时，交易员就会开始抛售他所持有的股票
Dialogue: 3,0:45:23.24,0:45:26.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's when traders will start selling the stocks he holds.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:26.60,0:45:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦交易员开始抛售..
Dialogue: 3,0:45:26.60,0:45:29.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And once traders start selling...
Dialogue: 4,0:45:30.32,0:45:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就会变成自由落体！
Dialogue: 3,0:45:30.32,0:45:32.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a free fall. Yes!
Dialogue: 4,0:45:33.04,0:45:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这次牛将被献祭
Dialogue: 3,0:45:33.04,0:45:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The bull will be sacrificed this time.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:37.28,0:45:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 怎么样，哈尔沙德兄弟?-欢迎
Dialogue: 3,0:45:37.28,0:45:39.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What's up Harshad Bhai? - Welcome.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:40.80,0:45:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了，吉涅什？
Dialogue: 3,0:45:40.80,0:45:42.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's up, Jignesh Bhai?
Dialogue: 4,0:45:42.28,0:45:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}报社记者来我家门口亲自传递消息！
Dialogue: 3,0:45:42.28,0:45:44.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ahmedabad Samachar at my doorstep delivering news personally!
Dialogue: 4,0:45:44.56,0:45:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你怎么知道的?-对记者来说没什么是秘密的
Dialogue: 3,0:45:44.56,0:45:47.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- How did you know? - Nothing is secret for a reporter.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:48.12,0:45:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你什么都知道
Dialogue: 3,0:45:48.12,0:45:50.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know everything about everything.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:50.60,0:45:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉我，标题是什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:45:50.60,0:45:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell me. What are the headlines?
Dialogue: 4,0:45:52.28,0:45:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马努的人正计划把你的名誉抛到九霄云外
Dialogue: 3,0:45:52.28,0:45:55.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai's people are planning to throw your reputation to the wind.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:56.00,0:45:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，他们会的
Dialogue: 3,0:45:56.00,0:45:57.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course, they will.
Dialogue: 4,0:45:57.40,0:46:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在他把SPIC拉到这么低，很明显他会庆祝一下
Dialogue: 3,0:45:57.40,0:46:00.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now that he's pulled SPIC so low, it's obvious he will celebrate a little.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:00.56,0:46:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随他去吧，我们马上就能扭转局势
Dialogue: 3,0:46:00.56,0:46:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let him. We will turn the tide in no time.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:03.40,0:46:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明天，马努的人将进一步拉低 SPIC
Dialogue: 3,0:46:03.40,0:46:05.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai's people are going to further target SPIC tomorrow.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:06.16,0:46:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这些吗，还是你有更多的消息？
Dialogue: 3,0:46:06.16,0:46:07.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is that it or you have some more news?
Dialogue: 4,0:46:09.16,0:46:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上的内幕消息是，你将无法与交易所保持平衡
Dialogue: 3,0:46:09.16,0:46:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The inside news in the market is that you won't be able to square up with the exchange.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:12.32,0:46:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}吉涅什兄弟，这不是内幕消息，这叫做谣言
Dialogue: 3,0:46:12.32,0:46:16.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Jignesh Bhai, that's not inside news. This is called a rumour.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:17.12,0:46:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们在证交所有一千万卢比资金
Dialogue: 3,0:46:17.12,0:46:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have a margin of one crore with BSE.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:20.28,0:46:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}赔点钱对我们来说不算什么
Dialogue: 3,0:46:20.28,0:46:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can easily cover the loss.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:22.56,0:46:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们就这么容易受骗吗? 他们会盲目地相信马努吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:46:22.56,0:46:26.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are people so gullible? That they will blindly believe Manu Bhai?
Dialogue: 4,0:46:26.36,0:46:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天，马努的谎言被视为福音真理
Dialogue: 3,0:46:26.36,0:46:30.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today, Manu Bhai's lies are taken as the gospel truth.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:31.56,0:46:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}考虑一下，我要走了
Dialogue: 3,0:46:31.56,0:46:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Think about it. I'll be off.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:33.96,0:46:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 留下喝点茶吧-下次吧
Dialogue: 3,0:46:33.96,0:46:36.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Stay. Have some tea. - Next time.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:36.48,0:46:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我还有事
Dialogue: 3,0:46:36.48,0:46:37.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have more news to deliver.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:38.88,0:46:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不怕马努，他没那么强大
Dialogue: 3,0:46:38.88,0:46:41.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not afraid of Manu Bhai. He's not that powerful.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:42.24,0:46:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当富人们在金房子里睡觉时..
Dialogue: 3,0:46:42.24,0:46:44.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}While the rich sleep in chambers of gold...
Dialogue: 4,0:46:44.24,0:46:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}穷人们在寒冷中熬夜
Dialogue: 3,0:46:44.24,0:46:45.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the poor stay up all night in the cold.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:45.96,0:46:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在说什么? 用我能听懂的语言说话
Dialogue: 3,0:46:45.96,0:46:48.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you saying? Speak in a language I understand.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:48.64,0:46:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟
Dialogue: 3,0:46:48.64,0:46:49.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:50.32,0:46:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不需要害怕马努
Dialogue: 3,0:46:50.32,0:46:52.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We don't need to fear Manu Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:52.44,0:46:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们应该害怕那些相信马努的人
Dialogue: 3,0:46:52.44,0:46:55.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We need to be afraid of the people who believe in Manu Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:55.88,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些担心一夜之间变穷的人
Dialogue: 3,0:46:55.88,0:46:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Those who are worried of becoming poor overnight.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:58.00,0:46:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马努无法摧毁我们
Dialogue: 3,0:46:58.00,0:46:59.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Manu Bhai cannot destroy us.
Dialogue: 4,0:46:59.96,0:47:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是那些因为这个谣言而失眠的软弱的人，可以摧毁我们
Dialogue: 3,0:46:59.96,0:47:04.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But those weak people who lose their sleep over this rumour, can destroy us.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:05.32,0:47:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，我建议我们尽可能地撤出来，越快越好
Dialogue: 3,0:47:05.32,0:47:09.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brother, I suggest we must pull back as much as we can, as soon as we can.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:09.52,0:47:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马努是冲着我们来的，他们拉低我们所持有的所有股票
Dialogue: 3,0:47:09.52,0:47:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are the target. They'll try to break every position that we're holding.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:12.52,0:47:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚你说的太简单了
Dialogue: 3,0:47:12.52,0:47:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan, what you're saying is not that easy.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:19.20,0:47:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德，我们得想想办法
Dialogue: 3,0:47:19.20,0:47:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, we need to think of something.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:23.64,0:47:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是要攻击我们的名声，对吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:47:23.64,0:47:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is after our reputation, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:47:26.60,0:47:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么只有一个办法可以拯救它
Dialogue: 3,0:47:26.60,0:47:28.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'There's only one way of saving it.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:29.04,0:47:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我们要还清所有欠款”
Dialogue: 3,0:47:29.04,0:47:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'We have to clear all our dues.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:31.16,0:47:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}准备支票结清所有的欠款
Dialogue: 3,0:47:31.16,0:47:32.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Let's prepare cheques to clear all payments.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:33.08,0:47:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“旁边还有一封信，上面写着... ”
Dialogue: 3,0:47:33.08,0:47:34.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And alongside, a letter that says...'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:35.04,0:47:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“忘掉违约，高摩提前14天清算债务”
Dialogue: 3,0:47:35.04,0:47:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...Forget default, Growmore is clearing off its dues 14 days in advance.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:39.16,0:47:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在市场开盘之前，让我们来见见玛雅大哥
Dialogue: 3,0:47:39.16,0:47:41.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And before the market opens, let's meet Mayya Bhai.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:41.64,0:47:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当证交所的执行董事宣布这一切都只是谣言... ..
Dialogue: 3,0:47:41.64,0:47:44.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'When the executive director of BSE announces that this is all just a rumour...'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:45.80,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 每个人的耳朵都会竖起来
Dialogue: 3,0:47:45.80,0:47:47.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...everyone's ears will perk up.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:48.32,0:47:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“所有的付款支票都已经签好了”
Dialogue: 3,0:47:48.32,0:47:50.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'All the payment cheques are ready with signature.'
Dialogue: 4,0:47:51.60,0:47:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}结算期为14天
Dialogue: 3,0:47:51.60,0:47:53.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The settlement period is of 14 days.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:54.28,0:47:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么这么早付款？
Dialogue: 3,0:47:54.28,0:47:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you clearing the payments so early?
Dialogue: 4,0:47:56.84,0:47:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为这事关名誉
Dialogue: 3,0:47:56.84,0:47:58.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because it's a matter of reputation.
Dialogue: 4,0:47:59.12,0:48:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们知道..
Dialogue: 3,0:47:59.12,0:48:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We know...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:00.60,0:48:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}通常人们会继续交易直到下一次结算
Dialogue: 3,0:48:00.60,0:48:03.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that normally people carry forward the trade till the next settlement...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:03.32,0:48:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后去找资金
Dialogue: 3,0:48:03.32,0:48:04.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and then go looking for funds.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:06.56,0:48:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是有些疯子在散布谣言..
Dialogue: 3,0:48:06.56,0:48:08.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But some people in BSE are spreading rumours...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:09.12,0:48:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说我们高摩没有资金
Dialogue: 3,0:48:09.12,0:48:10.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Growmore has no funds...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:10.92,0:48:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还说我们会拖欠款项
Dialogue: 3,0:48:10.92,0:48:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and that we would default on our payments.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:13.32,0:48:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是为什么我要提前结清所有的欠款
Dialogue: 3,0:48:13.32,0:48:15.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why I'm clearing all the dues in advance.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:15.48,0:48:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样一来，所有人都会明白，高摩并不缺乏资金
Dialogue: 3,0:48:15.48,0:48:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So that it becomes clear to all that Growmore is in no shortage of funds.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:19.52,0:48:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}麻雅兄弟，请张贴告示..
Dialogue: 3,0:48:19.52,0:48:22.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mayyaji, please put up a notice...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:23.12,0:48:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 说”高摩一切都很好”
Dialogue: 3,0:48:23.12,0:48:24.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...saying "Everything is fine at Growmore".
Dialogue: 4,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为如果那些散布谣言的人不闭嘴的话..
Dialogue: 3,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because, if the people spreading these rumours don't shut up...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:28.64,0:48:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么将会影响市场
Dialogue: 3,0:48:28.64,0:48:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then more than Harshad Mehta, this will affect the market.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:31.96,0:48:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能张贴告示
Dialogue: 3,0:48:31.96,0:48:33.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't put up a notice.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:33.96,0:48:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过别担心
Dialogue: 3,0:48:33.96,0:48:35.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But don't worry.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:35.64,0:48:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会告诉董事会，高摩已经提前支付了所有的款项
Dialogue: 3,0:48:35.64,0:48:39.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will tell the board that Growmore has paid all its dues in advance.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:39.36,0:48:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就市场而言..
Dialogue: 3,0:48:39.36,0:48:40.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And as far as the market goes...
Dialogue: 4,0:48:41.04,0:48:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别担心
Dialogue: 3,0:48:41.04,0:48:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:42.52,0:48:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}预算案通过后，市场动荡不安
Dialogue: 3,0:48:42.52,0:48:45.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market is quite shaken up after the budget.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:45.60,0:48:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们不会让任何人如此轻易地操纵市场，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:48:45.60,0:48:49.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we won't let anyone manipulate the market so easily, will we?
Dialogue: 4,0:48:49.44,0:48:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管是谁
Dialogue: 3,0:48:49.44,0:48:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whoever that may be.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:54.80,0:48:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大哥，我马上给吉涅什打电话
Dialogue: 3,0:48:54.80,0:48:56.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhai, I will call Jignesh right away.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:56.64,0:48:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这条消息明天应该会登在每个财经专栏上
Dialogue: 3,0:48:56.64,0:48:58.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This news should be in every financial column tomorrow.
Dialogue: 4,0:48:58.80,0:49:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果明天就出版，那就没有用了
Dialogue: 3,0:48:58.80,0:49:00.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It won't be of any use if it's published tomorrow.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:00.80,0:49:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这条消息必须在今天市场开盘前传达给人们
Dialogue: 3,0:49:00.80,0:49:03.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This news must reach people before the market opens today.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:04.08,0:49:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果有必要的话，我们要大声宣布我们已经付款了
Dialogue: 3,0:49:04.08,0:49:07.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If required, we'll scream from the rooftops that we have made the payment.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:07.56,0:49:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}会议怎么样，兄弟？
Dialogue: 3,0:49:07.56,0:49:08.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How was the meeting, brother?
Dialogue: 4,0:49:09.32,0:49:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘ 布尚... ’
Dialogue: 3,0:49:09.32,0:49:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Bhushan...'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:09.92,0:49:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从瓦法达茶馆到三明治摊，从午餐之家到咖啡馆
Dialogue: 3,0:49:09.92,0:49:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...from Wafadar Tea House to the sandwich stall, from the lunch home to Irani Cafe.'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:13.76,0:49:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像野火一样传播这个消息..
Dialogue: 3,0:49:13.76,0:49:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Spread this news like wildfire...
Dialogue: 4,0:49:15.48,0:49:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔已经付了钱
Dialogue: 3,0:49:15.48,0:49:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that Mehta has made the payment.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:17.12,0:49:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要拿任何人的钱
Dialogue: 3,0:49:17.12,0:49:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't take money from anyone.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:18.68,0:49:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}告诉大家今天哈尔沙德在餐厅请所有人喝茶
Dialogue: 3,0:49:18.68,0:49:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tell everyone that tea is on Harshad Mehta today.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:22.44,0:49:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他是证交所的阿米塔布·巴强（宝莱坞明星）
Dialogue: 3,0:49:22.44,0:49:24.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's the Bachchan of BSE.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:24.48,0:49:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁不认识他？
Dialogue: 3,0:49:24.48,0:49:25.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who doesn't know him?
Dialogue: 4,0:49:26.08,0:49:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德就代表着证交所，看看这个
Dialogue: 3,0:49:26.08,0:49:29.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}BSE means Harshad Mehta. Look at that.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:32.00,0:49:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}恭喜哈沙德 · 梅塔，茶算在哈尔沙德 · 巴伊身上
Dialogue: 3,0:49:32.00,0:49:34.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'CONGRATULATIONS TO HARSHAD MEHTA. TEA IS ON HARSHAD BHAI.'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:34.96,0:49:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个消息应该传到疯牛病的每一个角落
Dialogue: 3,0:49:34.96,0:49:37.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'This news should reach every nook and cranny of BSE...'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:37.72,0:49:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 哈尔沙德 · 梅塔不只是说说而已，他是在行动”
Dialogue: 3,0:49:37.72,0:49:40.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that Harshad Mehta doesn't just talk. He acts.'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:40.72,0:49:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“大力宣传这一信息，以至于没有人会怀疑梅塔兄弟的诚实”
Dialogue: 3,0:49:40.72,0:49:46.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Push the message so hard that nobody ever doubts the honesty of the Mehta Brothers.'
Dialogue: 4,0:49:46.44,0:49:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天哈尔沙德请客
Dialogue: 3,0:49:46.44,0:49:47.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tea is on Harshad Bhai today.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:48.08,0:49:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}免费? 什么情况？
Dialogue: 3,0:49:48.08,0:49:49.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Free? What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 4,0:49:50.76,0:49:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家都说哈沙德 · 巴伊破产了
Dialogue: 3,0:49:50.76,0:49:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone was saying that Harshad Bhai is bankrupt.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:54.48,0:49:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他已经提前支付了所有人的款项
Dialogue: 3,0:49:54.48,0:49:58.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he's cleared everyone's payments in advance.
Dialogue: 4,0:49:59.08,0:50:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 提前?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:49:59.08,0:50:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- In advance? - Yes.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:01.28,0:50:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让交易所的每一个经纪人都知道，现在是我们的时代了
Dialogue: 3,0:50:01.28,0:50:04.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Let every jobber and broker of BSE know that it's our time now.'
Dialogue: 4,0:50:07.20,0:50:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“任何人都不应该心存疑虑”
Dialogue: 3,0:50:07.20,0:50:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'There should be no doubt in anyone's mind.'
Dialogue: 4,0:50:09.88,0:50:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在梅塔的统治下，市场将陷入疯狂
Dialogue: 3,0:50:09.88,0:50:12.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'In Mehta's reign, the market will go insane.'
Dialogue: 4,0:50:22.52,0:50:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果哈尔沙德愿意的话，他可以等到协议期结束
Dialogue: 3,0:50:22.52,0:50:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad could have waited out the settlement period, if he wanted.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:26.60,0:50:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他没有
Dialogue: 3,0:50:26.60,0:50:28.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he didn't.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:29.68,0:50:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为了自己的名誉，他个人蒙受了巨大的损失
Dialogue: 3,0:50:29.68,0:50:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He incurred such a huge personal loss for the sake of his reputation.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:35.60,0:50:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人都在说，‘在梅塔的统治下，市场将变得疯狂’
Dialogue: 3,0:50:35.60,0:50:39.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone is saying, 'In Mehta's reign, the market will go insane.'
Dialogue: 4,0:50:41.40,0:50:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}疯狂？
Dialogue: 3,0:50:41.40,0:50:42.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Insane?
Dialogue: 4,0:50:43.44,0:50:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别像个傻瓜一样说话
Dialogue: 3,0:50:43.44,0:50:45.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't talk like a fool.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:46.64,0:50:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种疯狂不会持续很久的
Dialogue: 3,0:50:46.64,0:50:48.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This insanity won't last long.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:50.64,0:50:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个该死的家伙最后会一贫如洗
Dialogue: 3,0:50:50.64,0:50:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The f****r will end up naked.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:54.76,0:50:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}混蛋
Dialogue: 3,0:50:54.76,0:50:56.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}M**********r.
Dialogue: 4,0:50:56.60,0:50:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他能自己掏多久的腰包？
Dialogue: 3,0:50:56.60,0:50:58.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How long will he pay from his own pocket?
Dialogue: 4,0:51:09.88,0:51:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让马努见鬼去吧! 该死的眼镜蛇！
Dialogue: 3,0:51:09.88,0:51:12.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To hell with Manu! Bloody Cobra!
Dialogue: 4,0:51:12.76,0:51:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}原来你是只猫鼬
