Dialogue: 4,0:51:15.08,0:51:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}猫鼬的意思是... 眼镜蛇杀手
Dialogue: 3,0:51:15.08,0:51:16.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mongoose means... Cobra killer.
Dialogue: 4,0:51:16.96,0:51:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你就是眼镜蛇杀手，就连莫塔海今天也该感谢他了
Dialogue: 3,0:51:16.96,0:51:20.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You are the Cobra killer. Even MotaBhai must be thanking him today.
